ays%20be%20an%20integral%20and%20inalienable%20part%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20India%20said%20strongly%20rejecting%20China's%20objection.%20External%20affairs%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20the%20Chinese%20side%20has%20been%20made%20aware%20of%20this%20'consistent%20position'%20on%20several%20occasions.%20China%20on%20Monday%20said%20it%20lodged%20a%20diplomatic%20protest%20with%20India%20over%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20last%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamata%20Banerjee's%20%26quot%3BLudo%26quot%3B%20Barb%20At%20BJP%20Over%20Citizenship%20Law%2C%20And%20NRC%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20create%20unrest%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20yesterday's%20announcement%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BLudo%20move%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20an%20administrative%20meeting%20at%20Bengal's%20Habra%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20chief%20alleged%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20%26quot%3Bsnatch%20away%20citizenship%20rights%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20she%20doubts%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20law.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20clarity.%20It%20is%20a%20misleading%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20leaders%20say%20CAA%20gives%20you%20rights.%20But%20the%20moment%20you%20apply%20for%20citizenship%2C%20you%20become%20illegal%20migrants%20and%20you%20will%20lose%20your%20rights.%20You%20will%20lose%20rights%20and%20be%20taken%20to%20detention%20camps.%20Please%20think%20before%20you%20apply%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20assets%20of%20those%20people%20who%20don't%20get%20citizenship%3F%20This%20is%20BJP's%20game%20of%20Ludo%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20said%20the%20CAA's%20implementation%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20work%20on%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC).%20The%20NRC%20is%20a%20record%20of%20Indian%20citizens%20that%20has%20been%20implemented%20only%20in%20Assam%20so%20far.%20In%202019%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20said%20that%20a%20pan-India%20NRC%20was%20not%20on%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%2C%20CAA%20is%20linked%20to%20NRC.%20People%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20detention%20camps.%20I%20will%20not%20allow%20this%20to%20happen%20in%20Bengal.%20Have%20you%20ever%20heard%20of%20citizenship%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%3F%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20chief%20described%20the%20new%20law%20as%20%26quot%3Banother%20game%20to%20divide%20Bengal%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20let%20this%20happen.%20We%20are%20all%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20last%20evening%20issued%20a%20notification%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20under%20which%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20fleeing%20religious%20persecution%20can%20seek%20Indian%20citizenship.%20Persons%20from%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%2C%20Parsi%20or%20Christian%20communities%20from%20these%20countries%2C%20who%20entered%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20can%20seek%20citizenship%20under%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20criticised%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20which%20cleared%20the%20Parliament%20in%202019.%20They%20have%20pointed%20to%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20with%20the%20main%20Opposition%20Congress%20alleging%20a%20polarisation%20plan%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Trinamool%2C%20however%2C%20yesterday's%20announcement%20poses%20a%20bigger%20poll%20challenge.%20Implementation%20of%20CAA%20was%20a%20longstanding%20demand%20of%20Matuas%2C%20a%20Hindu%20scheduled%20caste%20group%20with%20roots%20in%20present-day%20Bangladesh.%20Most%20members%20of%20the%20community%20had%20entered%20Bengal%20after%20Partition%20or%20after%20Bangladesh%20was%20formed.%20The%20group%20is%20politically%20significant%2C%20and%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20Trinamool%20have%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20woo%20Matuas%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20state%20and%20national%20elections.%20The%20BJP%20now%20hopes%20that%20yesterday's%20announcement%20may%20tilt%20the%20scales%20in%20its%20favour.%20Following%20the%20announcement%20last%20evening%2C%20celebrations%20were%20held%20in%20areas%20dominated%20by%20the%20Matua%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20BJP%20MP%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Shantanu%20Thakur%20thanked%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20fulfilling%20the%20dream%20of%20three%20generations%20of%20Matuas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20the%20community%2C%20which%20supports%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20was%20sceptical.%20Mamatabala%20Thakur%2C%20a%20former%20MP%20from%20the%20party%2C%20said%20the%20Centre's%20announcement%20is%20aimed%20at%20getting%20votes.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20the%20citizenship%20rights%20already%20granted%20to%20Matuas%20after%201947%3F%20Will%20the%20CAA%20force%20them%20to%20come%20up%20with%20identity%20proofs%20once%20again%20and%20throw%20them%20into%20an%20uncertain%20future%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApparently%20referring%20to%20the%20seats%20dominated%20by%20the%20Matua%20community%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20this%20just%20to%20win%201%20or%202%20seats%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20you%20hand%20over%20your%20future%20to%20the%20BJP%20for%20an%20election%3F%20This%20is%20to%20harass%20people%20and%20win%20seats.%20My%20Matua%20brothers%20and%20sisters%2C%20do%20you%20believe%20in%20this%3F%20Will%20you%20be%20able%20to%20vote%3F%20Don't%20walk%20this%20path.%20BJP%20will%20say%20many%20things%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20lie%20and%20a%20jumla%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710234360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fqm3qh9ng_mamata-banerjee_625x300_10_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-ludo-barb-at-bjp-over-citizenship-law-and-nrc-warning-5223787%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20create%20unrest%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20yesterday's%20announcement%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BLudo%20move%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-ludo-barb-at-bjp-over-citizenship-law-and-nrc-warning-5223787%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-ludo-barb-at-bjp-over-citizenship-law-and-nrc-warning-5223787%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-ludo-barb-at-bjp-over-citizenship-law-and-nrc-warning-5223787%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vishal%20Mega%20Mart%20planning%20%241%20bn%20IPO%20valuing%20supermarket%20chain%20at%20%245%20bn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710234308000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F24%2Ffull%2F1700846880-3633.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Fvishal-mega-mart-planning-1-bn-ipo-valuing-supermarket-chain-at-5-bn-124031200458_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20retailer%20ha