ou're%20screened%20before%20you%20can%20move%20in%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cohabs%20team%20ensures%20you%20have%20the%20right%20vibe%20and%20are%20there%20for%20the%20right%20reasons%20before%20you%20can%20sign%20a%20lease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20questions%20were%20fairly%20straightforward%3A%20They%20asked%20my%20age%2C%20the%20reason%20I%20moved%20to%20New%20York%2C%20how%20I%20heard%20about%20Cohabs%2C%20what%20are%20my%20previous%20experiences%20with%20flatmates%2C%20and%20what%20are%20my%20hobbies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20sign%20a%20lease%20for%20six%20months%20or%20one%20year%2C%20and%20I%20chose%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHouse%20rules%20are%20written%20into%20the%20lease%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lease%20has%20some%20things%20you%20have%20to%20agree%20to%20that%20are%20above%20and%20beyond%20a%20typical%20lease%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20agree%20to%20pay%20our%20rent%20on%20time%2C%20be%20respectful%20of%20others%2C%20clean%20our%20room%20when%20we%20move%20out%20to%20receive%20our%20deposit%20back%2C%20keep%20common%20spaces%20organized%2C%20wash%20our%20dishes%2C%20organize%20for%20the%20team%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froam-co-coliving-coworking-commune-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehousekeepers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20respect%20each%20other%2C%20let%20our%20housemates%20know%20when%20we%20invite%20people%20over%2C%20take%20out%20the%20trash%2C%20and%20reduce%2C%20reuse%2C%20and%20recycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rent%20is%20fair%20to%20me%20for%20what%20I%20get%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20bedroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ef3ec0ce7f1785b2e88193%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20bedroom%20in%20a%20Cohabs%20house.%3Cp%3ECohabs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20pay%20%242%2C000%20a%20m