Ffriends-trivia-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%20the%20TV%20show%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20love%20having%20a%20little%20family%20in%20New%20York%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcohousing-single-moms-living-together-became-best-friends-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efriends%20I%20can%20count%20on%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20us%20are%20very%20far%20from%20our%20loved%20ones%20and%20are%20fairly%20new%20to%20New%20York.%20We%20have%20Americans%2C%20Spanish%2C%20English%2C%20and%20French%20among%20our%20nationalities.%20The%20age%20range%20is%2023%20to%2032%2C%20which%20sounds%20like%20a%20lot%20but%20works%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20night%20when%20I%20come%20home%20from%20work%2C%20people%20are%20in%20the%20kitchen%20making%20food%20and%20having%20meals%20together.%20That%20makes%20me%20really%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20kitchen%20in%20a%20Cohabs%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ef3f0dce7f1785b2e881c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20kitchens%20in%20a%20Cohabs%20house.%3Cp%3ECohabs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20feels%20better%20than%20a%20typical%20share%20house%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20super%20nervous%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20because%20I%20only%20knew%20one%20person%2C%20so%20moving%20into%20the%20house%20was%20a%20relief.%20My%20number%20one%20fear%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-loneliness-does-to-the-body-and-brain-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeeling%20lonely%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20this%20was%20the%20perfect%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22couches%20in%20a%20living%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ef3f456080194819feae2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20living%20room%20in%20a%20Cohabs%20house.%3Cp%3ECohabs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lived%20in%20shared%20flats%20and%20houses%20before%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-co-living-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esense%20of%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20here%20is%20much%20stronger.%20The%20Cohabs%20team%20really%20emphasizes%20this%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20first%20Sunday%20of%20every%20month%2C%20they%20send%20us%20a%20brunch%20for%20everyone%20to%20bond%20over.%20They%20also%20organize%20events%20like%20going%20rock%20climbing%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20respect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20adults%2C%20so%20we%20know%20how%20to%20live%20in%20a%20community%20and%20respect%20each%20other.%20I%20haven't%20seen%20any%20weird%20fights%20or%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20together%20has%20been%20easy%2C%20as%20we%20have%20similar%20lifestyles%2C%20but%20if%20you%20want%20to%20have%20people%20over%2C%20you%20do%20need%20to%20warn%20everyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20came%20to%20visit%20from%20Europe%2C%20and%20my%20parents%20were%20impressed%20with%20the%20house.%20They%20stayed%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%20but%20if%20my%20brother%20came%20alone%2C%20he%20probably%20would've%20stayed%20with%20me%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe've%20started%20some%20of%20our%20own%20traditions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Christmas%2C%20we%20put%20up%20a%20tree%20and%20hung%20pictures%20of%20our%20heads%20instead%20of%20ornaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20New%20Year's%20Eve%2C%20we%20all%20bought%20a%20tiny%20bottle%20of%20Champagne%20and%20told%20each%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-mistake-setting-new-years-resolutions-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20goal