ng%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohn%20Barnett%20worked%20for%20the%20US%20aerospace%20giant%20Boeing%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades%2C%20until%20his%20retirement.%20The%2062-year-old%20retired%20in%202017%2C%20on%20health%20grounds.%20After%20retiring%2C%20Barnett%20embarked%20on%20a%20long-running%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20before%20his%20death%2C%20Barnett%20had%20been%20giving%20evidence%20in%20a%20whistleblower%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20company.%20He%20worked%20as%20a%20quality%20manager%20at%20the%20North%20Charleston%20plant%20making%20the%20787%20Dreamliner%20from%202010.%20It%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20787%20Dreamliner%20is%20a%20state-of-the-art%20airliner%20used%20mainly%20on%20long-haul%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20John%20Barnett%20Revealed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202019%2C%20Barnett%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20BBC%20revealed%20that%20faulty%20parts%20were%20deliberately%20fitted%20to%20planes%20by%20a%20line%20of%20production%20workers%20at%20one%20of%20the%20Boeing%20factories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20uncovered%20some%20serious%20problems%20with%20the%20oxygen%20systems%2C%20which%20could%20even%20mean%20that%20one%20in%20four%20breathing%20masks%20wouldn't%20work%20during%20an%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarnett%20reportedly%20claimed%20that%20passengers%20on%20its%20787%20Dreamliner%20could%20be%20left%20without%20oxygen%20when%20the%20cabin%20suffered%20a%20sudden%20decompression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20a%20few%20tests%2C%20Barnett%20said%20that%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20oxygen%20systems%20could%20be%20faulty%20and%20might%20not%20work%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20test%20on%20emergency%20oxygen%20systems%2C%20Barnett%20found%20that%20the%20787%20Dreamliner%20showed%20a%20failure%20rate%20of%2025%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20get%20a%20new%20aircraft%20built%20the%20assembly%20process%20in%20South%20Carolina%20was%20rushed%2C%20leading%20to%20compromised%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20this%20but%20the%20workers%20also%20failed%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20components%20in%20the%20factory%2C%20allowing%20the%20defective%20components%20to%20go%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20even%20accused%20the%20firm%20of%20using%20sub-standard%20parts%20from%20the%20scrap%20bins%20and%20fitting%20it%20to%20the%20planes%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20prevent%20delays%20on%20the%20production%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20informed%20the%20managers%20about%20his%20concerns%2C%20no%20actions%20were%20taken.%20However%2C%20in%202017%2C%20a%20review%20by%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA)%2C%20the%20US%20regulator%2C%20did%20uphold%20some%20of%20Barnett's%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Boeing%20responded%20to%20these%20accusations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20Barnett's%20accusations%2C%20Boeing%20said%20that%20all%20its%20aircraft%20were%20built%20to%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20safety%20and%20quality.%C2%A0The%20company%20insisted%20that%20%26quot%3Bsafety%2C%20quality%20and%20integrity%20are%20at%20the%20core%20of%20Boeing's%20values%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710234060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F5d871q_john-barnett-_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjohn-barnett-death-john-barnett-dies-what-whistleblower-john-barnett-revealed-about-boeing-before-his-death-5223218%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Back%20in%202019%2C%20Mr%20Barnett%20said%20that%20faulty%20parts%20were%20deliberately%20fitted%20to%20planes%20by%20a%20line%20of%20production%20workers%20at%20one%20of%20the%20Boeing%20factories.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjohn-barnett-death-john-barnett-dies-what-whistleblower-john-barnett-revealed-about-boeing-before-his-death-5223218%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjohn-barnett-death-john-barnett-dies-what-whistleblower-john-barnett-revealed-about-boeing-before-his-death-5223218%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjohn-barnett-death-john-barnett-dies-what-whistleblower-john-barnett-revealed-about-boeing-before-his-death-5223218%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Divine%20Authoritarianism%20Is%20Not%20Good%20For%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09162606%2FUntitled-design-37.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20popular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY9253_M38Xk%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20by%20a%20young%20man%20named%20Dhruv%20Rathee%2C%20which%20irked%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20supporters.%20Its%20broad%20argument%20may%20be%20understood%20by%20the%20title%2C%20which%20was%20%E2%80%9CIs%20India%20becoming%20a%20dictatorship%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20examples%20used%20in%20the%20video%20included%20the%20recent%20rigging%20of%20the%20Chandigarh%20mayoral%20election%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20recent%20rigging%20of%20the%20panel%20to%20select%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%2C%20the%20misuse%20of%20government%20agencies%20against%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3Cb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dictionary%20defines%20dictatorship%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20form%20of%20government%20in%20which%20one%20person%20or%20a%20small%20group%20possesses%20absolute%20power%20without%20effective%20constitutional%20limitations%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Ca%20form%20of%20government%20in%20which%20absolute%20power%20is%20concentrated%20in%20an%20individual%20or%20a%20small%20clique%E2%80%9D.%20I%20will%20leave%20it%20to%20readers%20to%20see%20whether%20these%20definitions%20align%20with%20what%20is%20happening%20around%20us%20in%20India%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%E2%80%9Cdictator%E2%80%9D%2C%20like%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cfascist%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20overused%20and%20its%20real%20meaning%20may%20be%20lost%20as%20it%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20term%20of%20abuse%20rather%20than%20one%20of%20definition.%20When%20social%20scientist%20Ashish%20Nandy%20described%20meeting%20our%20present%20prime%20minister%20before%20he%20became%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20wrote%20the%20following%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20long%2C%20rambling%20interview%2C%20but%20it%20left%20me%20in%20no%20doubt%20that%20here%20was%20a%20classic%2C%20clinical%20case%20of%20a%20fascist.%20I%20never%20use%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98fascist%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20term%20of%20abuse%3B%20to%20me%20it%20is%20a%20diagnostic%20category%20comprising%20not%20only%20one%E2%80%99s%20ideological%20posture%20but%20also%20the%20personality%20traits%20and%20motivational%20patterns%20contextualising%20the%20ideology.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3ENandy%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CModi%2C%20it%20gives%20me%20no%20pleasure%20to%20tell%20readers%2C%20met%20virtually%20all%20the%20criteria%20that%20psychiatrists%2C%20psycho-analysts%20and%20psychologists%20had%20set%20up%20after%20years%20of%20empirical%20work%20on%20the%20authoritarian%20personality.%20He%20had%20the%20same%20mix%20of%20puritanical%20rigidity%2C%20narrowing%20of%20emotional%20life%2C%20massive%20use%20of%20the%20ego%20defence%20of%20projection%2C%20denial%20and%20fear%20of%20his%20own%20passions%20combined%20with%20fantasies%20of%20violence%20%E2%80%94%20all%20set%20within%20the%20matrix%20of%20clear%20paranoid%20and%20obsessive%20personality%20traits.%20I%20still%20remember%20the%20cool%2C%20measured%20tone%20in%20which%20he%20elaborated%20a%20theory%20of%20cosmic%20conspiracy%20against%20India%20that%20painted%20every%20Muslim%20as%20a%20suspected%20traitor%20and%20a%20potential%20terrorist.%20I%20came%20out%20of%20the%20interview%20shaken%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3Cb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20return%20to%20dictatorship%2C%20to%20my%20mind%20a%20less%20emotional%20and%20more%20reliable%20question%20is%20to%20ask%20whether%20we%20are%20under%20authoritarian%20rule.%20This%20is%20defined%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20lack%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20wishes%20or%20opinions%20of%20others%E2%80%9D.%20Now%2C%20let%20us%20look%20at%20some%20indicators%20to%20see%20if%20this%20is%20the%20case.%20What%20are%20they%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20is%20there%20any%20concern%20for%20the%20wishes%20and%20opinions%20of%20those%20inside%20the%20government%3F%20To%20answer%20that%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20two%20important%20cases%20where%20we%20have%20conclusive%20evidence.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20national%20lockdown%20of%20March%2024%2C%202020.%20The%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20filed%20240%20RTIs%20(right%20to%20information%20requests)%20one%20year%20after%20the%20lockdown%20to%20ask%20who%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%20knew%20the%20lockdown%20was%20being%20announced%20that%20evening.%20Was%20disaster%20management%20consulted%3F%20Or%20the%20finance%20ministry%20or%20health%20ministry%3F%20The%20answer%20from%20the%20government%20was%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%E2%80%9D.%20Nobody%20had%20been%20consulted%20or%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20demonetisation.%20On%20November%208%2C%202016%2C%20the%20cabinet%20was%20summoned%20and%20ministers%20told%20to%20not%20bring%20their%20mobile%20phones%2C%20meaning%20that%20they%20did%20not%20know%20till%20the%20prime%20minister%20told%20them%20that%20Rs%201%2C000%20and%20Rs%20500%20notes%20would%20be%20useless%20after%20that%20evening.%20Since%20the%20ministers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%2C%20the%20ministries%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20prepare%20for%20either%20of%20these%20events.%20Parliamentary%20forms%20of%20government%20function%20on%20something%20called%20collective%20responsibility.%20But%20not%20in%20New%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20head%20of%20state%20is%20instructed%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20Parliament%20because%20the%20prime%20minister%20wants%20to%20preside%20and%20protocol%20requires%20that%20the%20head%20of%20state%20be%20absent.%20Similarly%2C%20and%20for%20the%20same%20reason%2C%20the%20head%20of%20state%20is%20not%20asked%20to%20come%20to%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%20which%20the%20prime%20minister%20wants%20to%20preside%20over.%20This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20questioned%2C%20much%20less%20opposed%2C%20because%20the%20idea%20that%20only%20one%20individual%20represents%20the%20State%20has%20become%20accepted%20here.%20Have%20a%20look%20at%20his%20photograph%20everywhere%3B%20one%20cannot%20escape%20it.%20We%20need%20not%20spend%20much%20time%20going%20over%20what%20this%20government%20has%20done%20and%20is%20doing%20to%20the%20Opposition%2C%20by%20misusing%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%20There%20is%20a%20daily%20update%20on%20that.%20It%20is%20nobody%E2%80%99s%20case%20that%20there%20is%20any%20concern%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwishes%20and%20opinion%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20constitutional%20Opposition.%20Those%20in%20civil%20society%20who%20dissent%20have%20also%20seen%20they%20must%20go%20directly%20to%20jail%20because%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20tolerating%20what%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felectoral-bonds-narendra-modi-rbi%5C%22%3EModi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Tryst%20with%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Should%20Neither%20Be%20Forgotten%20Nor%20Forgiven%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20we%20must%20pay%20heed%20to%20what%20the%20world%20outside%20is%20saying%20about%20India%20on%20this%20subject.%20This%20month%2C%20the%20annual%20V-Dem%20Institute%E2%80%99s%20report%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Gothenburg%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20autocrat