%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20numbers%20are%20the%20growth%20rates%20of%20daily%20average%20users%2C%20or%20DAUs%2C%20for%20some%20of%20the%20popular%20social%20media%20services%20globally.%20This%20is%20from%20a%20quarterly%20review%20conducted%20by%20Evercore%20ISI%20analysts%20who%20tap%20Sensor%20Tower%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20demolishing%20the%20competition%20from%202020%20through%20the%20first%20half%20of%202022%2C%20TikTok's%20DAU%20growth%20rate%20has%20collapsed.%20In%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202023%2C%20the%20video%20service%20lagged%20Snapchat%2C%20YouTube%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-instagram-reels-tiktok-morgan-stanley-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Facebook.%20Yes%2C%20you%20read%20that%20right%3A%20The%20ancient%20big%20blue%20app%20grew%20faster%20than%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20going%20on%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20interesting%20theory%20is%20that%20TikTok%20users%20are%20growing%20up%20and%20taking%20on%20new%20responsibilities%20that%20leave%20less%20time%20to%20watch%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20app%20launched%2C%20it%20took%20the%20world%20by%20storm.%20Young%20kids%20and%20teenagers%20were%20especially%20drawn%20to%20the%20service's%20unique%20creator-friendly%20content%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tiktok-is-changing-music-industry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eculture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20say%20those%20users%20were%20about%2013%20when%20they%20first%20downloaded%20the%20app%20in%202016%20and%202017.%20Now%2C%20these%20people%20are%20at%20least%2020%20years%20old.%20They%20have%20full-time%20jobs%20or%20are%20studying%20at%20college.%20For%20many%2C%20their%20parents%20no%20longer%20do%20their%20laundry%2C%20coo