g%20about%20her%20new%20corporate%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20landing%20her%20first%20office%20role%20out%20of%20college%2C%20she%20posted%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40brielleybelly123%2Fvideo%2F7291443944347405614%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20video%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20describing%20how%20little%20time%20she%20had%20left%20each%20day%20for%20a%20personal%20life%20and%20basic%20chores.%20Older%20viewers%20harshly%20criticized%20Brielle%20for%20being%20naive%20and%20a%20host%20of%20other%20alleged%20failings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20now%20realize%20is%20that%20Brielle%20was%20probably%20just%20a%20heavy%20TikTok%20user%20who%20had%20recently%20grown%20up%20and%20realized%20she%20no%20longer%20had%20as%20much%20time%20for%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDeleting%20TikTok%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20this%20in%20my%20own%20life.%20My%20two%20kids%20have%20been%20huge%20fans%20of%20TikTok%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20older%20one%20is%20now%20in%20her%20second%20year%20of%20college%2C%20studying%20mechanical%20engineering.%20She%20rents%20a%20house%20with%20friends.%20There's%20a%20huge%20study%20load%2C%20along%20with%20house%20cleaning%2C%20cooking%2C%20doing%20the%20dishes%2C%20emptying%20the%20trash%2C%20paying%20bills%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20delete%20TikTok%20from%20her%20phone.%20She's%20part%20of%20a%20competition%20in%20her%20house%20right%20now%20to%20see%20who%20can%20limit%20screen%20time%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20ago%2C%20this%20daughter%20watched%20at%20least%20two%20hours%20of%20TikTok%20per%20day.%20I'd%20given%20up%20trying%20to%20limit%20this.%20She's%20an%20adult%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20sway%20anymore.%20And%20yet%2C%20she%20recently%20came%20to%20the%20realization%20by%20herself%20that%20she%20couldn't%20fit%20in%20all%20her%20new%20obligations%20and%20still%20watch%20TikTok%20for%20hours%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20younger%20daughter%20lives%20at%20home%20and%20is%20still%20in%20high%20school%2C%20so%20her%20daily%20TikTok%20intake%20is%20still%20massive.%20She's%20leaving%20for%20college%20in%20the%20fall%2C%20so%20she'll%20eventually%20face%20a%20similar%20dilemma%20with%20her%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThis%20is%20not%20just%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20recently%20interviewed%20a%20few%20TikTok%20users%20in%20their%2020s.%20They%20tell%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fpersonal-tech%2Fquitting-tiktok-less-swiping-more-sleeping-1e166a39%3Fmod%3Dtech_feat2_personal-tech_pos1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20similar%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20They%20started%20noticing%20that%20TikTok%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20got%20in%20the%20way%20of%20sleep%2C%20work%2C%20household%20chores%2C%20and%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20many%20of%20their%20friends%20have%20deleted%20the%20app%20or%20scaled%20back%20their%20use%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeilah%20Bruce%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20accountant%2C%20told%20the%20Journal%20she%20stopped%20using%20TikTok%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20at%20a%20good%20place%20now%20with%20my%20friends%2C%20my%20family%2C%20my%20dishes%2C%20and%20my%20laundry%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20sacrifice%20those%20things%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTikTok%20offers%20several%20tools%2C%20from%20custom%20screen-time%20limits%20to%20sleep%20reminders%2C%20that%20are%20used%20by%20millions%20of%20people%20to%20help%20them%20make%20intentional%20decisions%20about%20how%20they%20spend%20their%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20TikTok%20spokeswoman%20told%20the%20Journal%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20app%20regularly%20reminds%20people%20of%20these%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.