f%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20four-and-a-half-year%20alliance%20with%20the%20Jannayak%20Janata%20Party%20(JJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJJP%2C%20which%20emerged%20from%20a%20split%20in%20the%20Chautala%20family%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20fought%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20against%20the%20BJP%20but%20later%20came%20on%20board%20to%20form%20an%20alliance%20after%20the%20latter%20fell%20short%20of%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20differences%20in%20seat%20allotment%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20core%20reason%20for%20the%20rift%20in%20the%20BJP-JJP%20alliance%2C%20which%20has%20been%20under%20strain%20for%20the%20past%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20sources%20indicate%20that%20the%20BJP%20Haryana%20cadre%20was%20also%20discontent%20with%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20JJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20recent%20decision%20to%20split%20from%20the%20JJP%20and%20form%20a%20new%20government%20was%20done%20to%20counter%20anti-incumbency%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections.%20The%20move%20was%20also%20aimed%20at%20splitting%20the%20dominant%20jat%20votes%20by%20leaving%20the%20JJP%20on%20its%20own%20and%20let%20it%20compete%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20jat%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20BJP%20won%20all%2010%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20But%20it%20remains%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20party%20to%20repeat%20its%20last%20election%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20immediately%20after%20the%20general%20election%2C%20Haryana%20will%20hold%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20possible%20change%20in%20leadership%2C%20BJP%20will%20also%20try%20to%20neutralise%20the%20growing%20unpopularity%20against%20Khattar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20chief%20minister%20for%20the%20last%20nine-and-a-half%20years%2C%20and%20hope%20that%20a%20Gujarat-like%20move%20will%20help%20them%20stay%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20BJP%20also%20changed%20government%20months%20before%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependents%20extend%20support%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%2C%20which%20currently%20has%2041%20MLAs%20in%20the%2090-member%20state%20assembly%2C%20needs%20support%20of%20five%20more%20MLAs%20to%20remain%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20all%20five%20independent%20MLAs%20have%20already%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Besides%2C%20Sirsa%20MLA%20and%20President-Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%2C%20Gopal%20Kanda%2C%20too%2C%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanda%2C%20in%20a%20media%20statement%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20the%20alliance%20(BJP-JJP)%20has%20almost%20broken.%20Even%20without%20the%20JJP%2C%20the%20Haryana%20government%20will%20stay%2C%20and%20all%20independent%20candidates%20will%20continue%20to%20support%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20many%20of%20these%20independents%20may%20be%20rewarded%20with%20a%20cabinet%20berth%20in%20the%20new%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Kanwar%20Pal%20Gujjar%20confirmed%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20cabinet%20ministers%20have%20resigned%2C%20and%20the%20governor%20has%20accepted%20the%20resignations.%20The%20next%20move%20will%20be%20determined%20after%20the%20legislative%20party%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710233142000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14121527%2FF3T6TBIb0AAY7VK.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-cm-manohar-lal-khattar-resigns-amid-rift-between-bjp-jjp-alliance-over-seat-sharing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20along%20with%20his%20cabinet%2C%20resigned%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20March%2012%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20initiated%20the%20process%20f