0experts%20alike.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F03%2F11%2Flifestyle%2F10-foot-mysterious-metal-monolith-appears-on-remote-uk-hill%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%2010-foot-tall%20block%20of%20steel%2C%20which%20is%20shaped%20like%20a%20giant%20Toblerone%2C%20was%20spotted%20by%20locals%C2%A0on%20Hay%20Bluff%20near%20the%20Powys%20town%20at%20the%20weekend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20thought%20it%20looked%20a%20bit%20bizarre%20and%20might%20be%20a%20scientific%20media%20research%20thing%20collecting%20rainwater%2C%E2%80%9D%20Richard%20Haynes%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walesonline.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fwales-news%2Fgiant-monolith-appears-top-welsh-28795875%5C%22%3EWales%20Online%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20realized%20it%20was%20way%20too%20tall%20and%20strange%20for%20that.%20Then%20I%20went%20up%20to%20it%20and%20it%20was%20about%2010-foot-tall%20at%20least%20and%20triangular%2C%20definitely%20stainless%20steel.%20It%20was%20hollow%20and%20I%20imagine%20pretty%20light.%20Light%20enough%20for%20two%20people%20to%20carry%20it%20up%20and%20plant%20it%20in%20the%20ground%2C''%20Mr%20Haynes%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pictures%20of%20the%20monolith%20that%20have%20gone%20viral%2C%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNickHintonn%2Fstatus%2F1767454707033739741%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Eevoked%20several%20conspiracy%20theories%3C%2Fa%3E%20online.%20While%20many%20said%20it%20was%20the%20work%20of%20aliens%2C%20others%20were%20convinced%20that%20it%20was%20an%20elaborate%20piece%20of%20undercover%20artwork.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20unusual%20sighting%2C%20a%20string%20of%20monoliths%20has%20appeared%20across%20the%20world%2C%C2%A0becoming%20the%20subject%20of%20intense%20public%20curiosity%20and%20speculation.%C2%A0Theories%20about%20their%20origins%20ranged%20from%20a%20marketing%20ploy%20to%20extraterrestrials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20a%20mysterious%2010-foot-tall%20metal%20slab%20appeared%20in%20southeastern%20Turkey%2C%20then%20quietly%20disappeared%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2021%2F02%2F10%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fturkey-monolith.html%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20was%20inscribed%20with%20a%20cryptic%20message%20in%20the%20Gokturk%20alphabet%2C%20an%20ancient%20Turkic%20language%2C%20''Look%20at%20the%20sky%2C%20see%20the%20moon.''%20It%20later%C2%A0turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20government%20publicity%20stunt%20to%20promote%20Turkey's%20new%20space%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20similar%20structures%20were%20found%20in%20Utah%20and%20California%20in%202020%20and%20were%20found%20to%20be%20the%20works%20of%20an%20artist%20group%20based%20in%20New%20Mexico.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2020%2F12%2F06%2Fa-fourth-monolith-has-been-found-on-the-isle-of-wight%2F%5C%22%3E10-foot-tall%20silver%20monolith%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20spotted%20on%20the%20Isle%20of%20Wight%2C%20attracting%20several%20locals%20who%20flocked%20to%20the%20site%20to%20catch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20massive%20steel%20monolith%20appeared%20in%20Romania%20in%20November%202020%2C%20and%20the%20government%20said%20it%20was%20unknown%20who%20put%20it%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710232920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Frbngq7fg_steel-monolith-_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgiant-mysterious-steel-monolith-spotted-on-remote-uk-hill-sparks-speculation-5223626%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2010-foot-tall%20block%20of%20steel%2C%20which%20is%20shaped%20like%20a%20giant%20Toblerone%2C%20was%20spotted%20by%20locals%20on%20Hay%20Bluff%20near%20the%20Powys%20town.%22%2