0of%20Israel%20after%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20the%20deadliest%20in%20the%20country's%20history.%20The%20US%20president%20worked%20closely%20with%20Netanyahu%20to%20deliver%20sweeping%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20support.%20But%20with%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20dead%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%2C%20and%20Israel%20planning%20an%20assault%20on%20Rafah%2C%20the%20last%20major%20city%20in%20the%20enclave%20where%20residents%20are%20sheltering%2C%20tensions%20between%20the%20Israeli%20leader%20and%20his%20most%20important%20ally%20over%20the%20civilian%20death%20toll%20have%20become%20impossible%20to%20conceal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20caught%20on%20a%20hot%20mic%20Thursday%20telling%20a%20legislator%20that%20he%20planned%20a%20%26quot%3Bcome-to-Jesus%26quot%3B%20meeting%20with%20Netanyahu.%20That%20came%20just%20days%20after%20his%20administration%20hosted%20Benny%20Gantz%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Israel's%20war%20cabinet%20but%20also%20Netanyahu's%20main%20political%20rival%2C%20for%20top-level%20meetings%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20leader%20smelled%20betrayal.%20%26quot%3BTo%20the%20extent%20that%20Hamas%20believes%20that%20there's%20daylight%20between%20us%2C%20that%20doesn't%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20told%20Fox%20News%20Monday.%20Hamas%20has%20been%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20kept%20up%20the%20flow%20of%20weapons%20and%20other%20support%20to%20Israel%2C%20even%20as%20it%20steps%20in%20to%20deliver%20humanitarian%20aid%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%2081%2C%20and%20Netanyahu%2C%2074%2C%20have%20differed%20for%20decades.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20the%20tensions%20are%20even%20more%20real.%20The%20US%20argues%20Israel%20isn't%20doing%20enough%20to%20limit%20death%20and%20suffering%20among%20the%20millions%20of%20ordinary%20Pale