2%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4iO2VqQnv4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20TVK%20Vijay%20(%40tvkvijayhq)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftvkvijayhq%2Fstatus%2F1767241944932237340%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20law%20like%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%20is%20not%20acceptable%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20live%20with%20social%20harmony.%20The%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20must%20assure%20that%20they%20will%20not%20implement%20the%20law%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay's%20TVK%20party%20will%20not%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20despite%20his%20political%20plunge%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%20He%20has%20announced%20that%20the%202026%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20be%20his%20party's%20first%20electoral%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20similar%20views%2C%20another%20South%20star%2C%20Kamal%20Haasan%2C%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20trying%20to%20divide%20people%20and%20destroy%20the%20harmony%20of%20India%20before%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20its%20desperation%20to%20win%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20Government%20has%20hurriedly%20notified%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20elections.%20The%20timing%20of%20the%20notification%20is%20more%20questionable%2C%20considering%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20determining%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20this%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Haasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Haasan%20said%20his%20outfit%20Makkal%20Needhi%20Maiam%20(MNM)%20has%20%26quot%3Bunwaveringly%20opposed%20the%20Act%2C%20legally%20and%20politically%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20the%20first%20party%20to%20challenge%20the%20CAA%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20try%20to%20divide%20our%20citizens%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%