d%20by%20suicide%20after%20being%20tolled%20by%20the%20social%20media%20cell%20of%20the%20Telegu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%20(JSP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20YSR%20Congress%20Party's%20event%20on%20March%204%2C%20Gothi%20Geethanjali%20Devi%20had%20spoken%20about%20receving%20a%20plot%20under%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government's%20'Jagananna%20Housing%20Scheme'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20that%20had%20gone%20viral%2C%20Geethanjali%20Devi%20had%20said%20she%20was%20a%20beneficiary%20of%20multiple%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20the%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy's%20government.%20%26quot%3BMy%20dream%20has%20come%20true%20today%20as%20the%20house%20site%20is%20now%20in%20my%20name.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20as%20I%20did%20not%20expect%20to%20receive%20it%20on%20the%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20Geetanjali%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20she%20was%20trolled%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20some%20using%20derogatory%20words%20for%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20Guntur%20Government%20Hospital%20where%20she%20died%20during%20the%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeetanjali%20is%20survived%20by%20two%20school-going%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20she%20was%20distressed%20due%20to%20the%20vicious%20attacks%20and%20hence%20she%20jumped%20before%20a%20running%20train.%20%26quot%3BUnable%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20constant%20trolling%2C%20Geethanjali%20reportedly%20went%20to%20the%20Tenali%20Railway%20Station%20on%20March%207%2C%20and%20jumped%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Janmabhoomi%20Express%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20Women%20Commission's%20former%20chairperson%20Vasavi%20Padma%20said%20stringent%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20social%20media%20handles%20that%20targeted%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeetanjali%20had%20said%20she%20would%20vote%20to%20make%20Chief%20Minister%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20