movies%2Fnews%2Flate-sidhu-moose-walas-father-balkaur-singh-breaks-his-silence-amid-the-pregnancy-rumours-of-his-wife-charan-kaur%2Farticleshow%2F108427322.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Russia%20In%20Talks%20To%20Develop%20%26quot%3BWorld's%20Most%20Powerful%20Fusion%20Reactor%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Russia%20are%20in%20discussions%20to%20collaborate%20on%20a%20range%20of%20activities%20including%20research%20on%20controlled%20thermonuclear%20fusion%20and%20joint%20development%20of%20the%20transit%20potential%20of%20the%20Northern%20Sea%20route%2C%20a%20top%20official%20of%20the%20state-run%20atomic%20energy%20corporation%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Rosatom%2C%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAE%20Likhacheva%2C%20CEO%20of%20Rosatom%20said%20the%20main%20topic%20of%20discussion%20with%20India%20was%20on%20the%20prospects%20of%20further%20cooperation%20in%20the%20field%20of%20nuclear%20technologies%20and%20in%20non-energy%20and%20non-nuclear%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikhacheva%2C%20who%20visited%20the%20Kudankulam%20Nuclear%20Power%20Plant%20(KNPP)%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20last%20month%2C%20said%20both%20sides%20have%20gained%20enormous%20experience%20in%20cooperation%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20KNPP's%20first%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlready%2C%20our%20cooperation%20extends%20beyond%20the%20borders%20of%20India.%20Indian%20companies%20are%20participating%20in%20Rosatom's%20project%20to%20build%20the%20first%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20in%20Bangladesh%20-%20Rooppur%20NPP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20in%20an%20email%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Rosatom%20was%20developing%20a%20considerable%20number%20of%20new%20areas%20of%20activity%20--about%2080%20of%20them--and%20in%20many%20of%20them%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20share%20its%20developments%20with%20friendly%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20we%20can%20offer%20the%20Indian%20side%20our%20competencies%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20low-power%20nuclear%20power%20plants%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%20both%20countries%20have%20great%20potential%20for%20cooperation%20in%20scientific%20research%2C%20including%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20controlled%20thermonuclear%20fusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikacheva%20said%20Rosatom%20was%20also%20ready%20to%20provide%20Indian%20scientists%2C%20the%20opportunity%20to%20conduct%20research%20at%20the%20MBIR%20multi-purpose%20fast%20neutron%20research%20reactor%20currently%20under%20construction%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20the%20most%20powerful%20research%20reactor%20in%20the%20world%2C%20it%20will%20open%20up%20unique%20opportunities%20for%20conducting%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20work%20on%20medical%20topics%2C%20research%20in%20the%20field%20of%20fundamental%20and%20applied%20physics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20creating%20new%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20that%2C%20Russia%20is%20also%20in%20discussions%20with%20India%20on%20the%20joint%20development%20of%20the%20transit%20potential%20of%20the%20Northern%20Sea%20Route%2C%20which%20is%20operated%20by%20Rosatom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20help%20ensure%20supplies%20of%20Russian%20oil%2C%20coal%20and%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20to%20India%20via%20the%20said%20route%2C%20with%20transshipment%20in%20Russian%20Far%20Eastern%20ports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20exploring%20options%20for%20cooperation%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20Euro-Asian%20Container%20Transit%20project.%20This%20project%20involves%20the%20organization%20of%20a%20pilot%20line%20for%20international%20container%20transit%20through%20the%20Northern%20Sea%20Route.%20As%20you%20can%20see%2C%20the%20range%20of%20areas%20for%20mutually%20beneficial%20cooperation%20is%20very%20wide%2C%20and%20I%20am%20confident%20we%20will%20still%20make%20a%20significant%20contribution%20to%20the%20development%20of%20the%20strategic%20partnership%20of%20our%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20India's%20long-term%20energy%20strategy%20and%20goals%2C%20the%20Rosatom%20CEO%20said%20that%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20have%20a%20cumulative%20installed%20capacity%20share%20of%20non-fossil%20fuel%20energy%20sources%20of%20around%2050%20per%20cent%20by%202030%20and%20achieve%20net-zero%20emissions%20by%202050.%20Nuclear%20energy%20would%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20attaining%20those%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India%20already%20ranks%20second%20after%20China%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20of%20nuclear%20power%20units%20under%20construction%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20KNPP%20is%20a%20flagship%20project%20of%20Indo-Russian%20cooperation%20and%20it%20is%20being%20built%20according%20to%20a%20modern%20generation%203%20design%20with%20VVER-1000%20reactors%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20largest%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20in%20India.%20Operating%20just%20one%201%2C000%20MW%20unit%20prevents%20on%20average%20more%20than%203%20million%20tons%20of%20CO2%20emissions%20annually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20the%20operation%20of%20the%20first%20two%20units%20has%20already%20prevented%20emissions%20of%20more%20than%2047%20million%20tons%20of%20CO2%20equivalent.%20This%20means%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20providing%20the%20south%20of%20India%20with%20the%20necessary%20electricity%2C%20the%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20is%20already%20helping%20to%20improve%20the%20environmental%20situation%20in%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20Likhacheva%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Unit%201%20and%202%20of%20the%20NPP%20were%20operating%20stably%20and%20in%20compliance%20with%20all%20safety%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20construction%20of%20the%20second%20stage%20(blocks%203%20and%204)%20and%20the%20third%20stage%20(blocks%205%20and%206)%20is%20actively%20underway.%20The%20construction%20process%20of%20the%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20is%20in%20full%20swing.%20Let%20me%20remind%20you%2C%20the%20Russian%20side's%20area%20of%20responsibility%20includes%20design%2C%20supply%20of%20main%20and%20auxiliary%20equipment%2C%20installation%20supervision%20and%20personnel%20training.%20We%20fulfill%20all%20our%20obligations%20in%20full%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikhacheva%20also%20said%20Rosatom%20has%20already%20delivered%20the%20first%20batches%20of%20the%20new%20type%20of%20fuel%20assemblies%2C%20TVS-2M%2C%20with%20an%20increased%20nuclear%20fuel%20load%2C%20to%20the%20power%20plant%20in%20June%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOperating%20on%20longer%20fuel%20cycles%20increases%20the%20economic%20efficiency%20of%20a%20nuclear%20plant%2C%20since%20the%20unit%20is%20shut%20down%20less%20frequently%20for%20scheduled%20maintenance.%20This%20increases%20the%20utilization%20factor%20of%20the%20installed%20capacity%20of%20the%20nuclear%20power%20plant%2C%20that%20is%2C%20it%20allows%20the%20nuclear%20plant%20to%20produce%20more%20electricity%20during%20the%20calendar%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20unit%20of%20KNPP%20will%20get%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20the%20new%20fuel%20assemblies%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikhacheva%20said%20nuclear%20energy%20certainly%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20climate%20change%20and%20its%20share%20in%20the%20global%20energy%20balance%20needs%20to%20be%20increased%2C%20because%20it%20has%20undeniable%20advantages%20compared%20to%20other%20low-carbon%20energy%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENuclear%20energy%20has%20one%20feature%20that%20greatly%20distinguishes%20it%20from%20other%20types%20of%20generation--cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20high%20level%20of%20costs%20at%20the%20construction%20stage%20is%20offset%20by%20a%20very%20long%20%E2%80%93%20currently%20up%20to%2080%20years%20%E2%80%93%20service%20life%2C%20during%20which%20the%20cost%20of%20electricity%20production%20is%20constantly%20decreasing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20nuclear%20energy%20is%20rightfully%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20affordable%20and%20most%20efficient%20types%20of%20electricity%20generation%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rosatom%20CEO%20further%20said%20Russian%20nuclear%20power%20units%20fully%20comply%20with%20all%20the%20requirements%20for%20modern%20nuclear%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20evidenced%20by%20the%20global%20demand%20for%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20of%20Russian%20design.%20Today%2C%20Rosatom%20projects%20account%20for%2088%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20exported%20construction%20of%20nuclear%20power%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710228600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-03%2Fnuclear-reactor-istock_650x400_51490779852.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-russia-in-talks-over-joint-thermonuclear-fusion-russian-atomic-body-chief-5222820%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20Russia%20are%20in%20discussions%20to%20collaborate%20on%20a%20range%20of%20activities%20including%20research%20on%20controlled%20thermonuclear%20fusion%20and%20joint%20development%20of%20the%20transit%20potential%20of%20the%20Northern%20Sea%20route.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-russia-in-talks-over-joint-thermonuclear-fusion-russian-atomic-body-chief-5222820%22%2C%2