r-for-ipl-injured-pacer-mohammed-shami-ruled-out-bcci%2Farticleshow%2F108426788.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%20After%20Centre%20Implements%20Citizenship%20Law%2C%20A%20Challenge%20In%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20Centre%20notified%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20rules%2C%20the%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%20(IUML)%20today%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20challenge%20the%20move.%C2%A0The%20party%2C%20primarily%20based%20in%20Kerala%2C%20has%20sought%20a%20pause%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20law%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20passed%20in%202019%2C%20enables%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20fleeing%20religious%20persecution%20to%20seek%20Indian%20citizenship.%20Persons%20from%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%2C%20Parsi%20or%20Christian%20communities%20from%20these%20countries%2C%20who%20entered%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20can%20seek%20citizenship%20under%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IUML%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20challenge%20the%20law%20in%202019.%20Its%20petition%20contends%20that%20not%20including%20Muslims%20in%20the%20list%20of%20those%20eligible%20for%20citizenship%20violates%20the%20right%20to%20equality%20under%20Article%2014%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20IUML%20had%20sought%20a%20pause%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20but%20the%20Centre%20had%20then%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20law%20will%20not%20come%20into%20force%20because%20the%20rules%20had%20not%20been%20notified%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20has%20said%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20CAA%20rules%20must%20be%20paused%20till%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20rules%20on%20250%20pending%20petitions%20against%20the%20Constitutional%20validity%20of%20the%20Act.%C2%A0The%20preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution%20envisages%20that%20India%20is%20a%20secular%20country%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20any%20law%20passed%20has%20to%20be%20religion-neutral%2C%20the%20petition%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre's%20announcement%20last%20evening%20prompted%20celebrations%2C%20as%20well%20as%20protests%2C%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Members%20of%20the%20Matua%20community%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Sindhi%20refugees%20living%20in%20Bhopal%20held%20celebrations%20after%20the%20announcement.%20In%20some%20other%20areas%2C%20however%2C%20the%20public%20mood%20was%20different.%20Protests%20erupted%20in%20Assam%2C%20which%20has%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20new%20citizenship%20rules%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20large-scale%20migration%20into%20the%20border%20state.%20In%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20country%2C%20protesters%20alleged%20that%20the%20law%20is%20discriminatory%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20targeted%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20over%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20Act's%20implementation%3A%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20polarise%20voters%20in%20Assam%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20them%204%20years%20and%203%20months%20to%20bring%20this%20rule.%20The%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20December%202019.%20The%20law%20should%20have%20been%20formed%20within%203-6%20months.%20Modi%20Government%20sought%20nine%20extensions%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20took%204%20years%20and%203%20months%20before%20notifying%20the%20rules%20last%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20just%20for