%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Begins%20Withdrawing%20Troops%20From%20Maldives%20Amid%20Strained%20Ties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20begun%20withdrawing%20military%20personnel%20operating%20surveillance%20aircraft%20in%20the%20Maldives%20after%20the%20new%20pro-China%20president%20ordered%20them%20to%20leave%2C%20local%20media%20reported%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mihaaru%20newspaper%20reported%20that%2025%20Indian%20troops%20deployed%20in%20the%20southernmost%20atoll%20of%20Addu%20had%20left%20the%20archipelago%20ahead%20of%20March%2010%2C%20the%20official%20start%20of%20the%20withdrawal%20agreed%20by%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20came%20to%20power%20in%20September%20on%20a%20pledge%20to%20kick%20out%20Indian%20security%20personnel%20deployed%20in%20the%20Maldives%20to%20patrol%20its%20vast%20maritime%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20talks%20with%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20had%20agreed%20to%20complete%20a%20withdrawal%20of%2089%20Indian%20troops%20and%20their%20support%20staff%20from%20the%20nation%20of%201%2C192%20tiny%20coral%20islands%20by%20May%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihaaru%20said%20the%20three%20Indian%20aircraft%20--%20two%20helicopters%20and%20one%20fixed-wing%20plane%20--%20will%20be%20operated%20by%20Indian%20civilian%20staff%2C%20who%20have%20already%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20official%20confirmation%20from%20either%20the%20Maldivian%20or%20Indian%20authorities%2C%20but%20Mihaaru%20said%20the%20Maldivian%20National%20Defence%20Force%20confirmed%20the%20Indian%20withdrawal%20had%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Maldives%20signed%20a%20%26quot%3Bmilitary%20assistance%26quot%3B%20deal%20with%20China%20as%20the%20Indians%20prepared%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldivian%20defence%20ministry%20said%20the%20deal%20was%20to%20foster%20%26quot%3Bstronger%20bilateral%20ties%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20China%20would%20train%20its