%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20are%20investigating%20Barnett's%20death.%20He%20worked%20for%20about%2032%20years%20at%20Boeing%20before%20retiring%20in%202017%2C%20and%20for%20a%20time%2C%20was%20a%20quality%20manager%20at%20a%20North%20Charleston%20manufacturing%20plant%20for%20the%20787%20Dreamliner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20post%2C%20Barnett%20said%20he%20observed%20worrying%20signs%20of%20slipping%20standards%20at%20Boeing%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20manufacturer%20was%20rushing%20to%20assemble%20its%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20seen%20a%20plane%20out%20of%20Charleston%20yet%20that%20I'd%20put%20my%20name%20on%20saying%20it's%20safe%20and%20airworthy%2C%26quot%3B%20Barnett%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F04%2F20%2Fbusiness%2Fboeing-dreamliner-production-problems.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-50293927%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20test%20in%202016%20for%20300%20oxygen%20systems%20showed%20that%20a%20quarter%20of%20them%20failed%20to%20deploy.%20Barnett%20also%20alleged%20that%20he%20knew%20of%20at%20least%20one%20case%20at%20the%20plant%20where%20workers%20used%20parts%20from%20scrap%20bins%20to%20fit%20planes%20on%20the%20production%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Barnett%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tmz.com%2F2024%2F01%2F31%2Fboeing-quality-manager-john-barnett-plane-alaska-airlines-window%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20TMZ%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20cases%20where%20inspectors%20were%20given%20only%20two%20hours%20to%20find%20defects%20in%20a%20supplier's%20products%2C%20significantly%20hampering%20their%20ability%20to%20conduct%20proper%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20denied%20Barnett's%20allegations%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2020-01-28%2Fboeing-whistleblower-dreamliner-production-issues-safety-threat%2F11904396%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20it%20found%20some%20defective%20oxygen%20systems%2C%20as%20Barnett%20reported%2C%20it%20removed%20them%20from%20production%20so%20they%20weren't%20deployed%20on%20any%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20visited%20the%20Charleston%20facility%20and%20found%20that%20more%20than%2050%20%26quot%3Bnon-conforming%26quot%3B%20parts%20were%20missing%2C%20appearing%20to%20add%20credibility%20to%20Barnett's%20claims%20of%20parts%20from%20scrap%20bins%20being%20used%2C%20per%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBarnett%20was%20due%20to%20continue%20deposition%2C%20lawyer%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBarnett%20had%20filed%20an%20AIR21%20case%20against%20Boeing%2C%20saying%20it%20undermined%20his%20career%20because%20he%20had%20raised%20safety%20concerns%20at%20the%20Charleston%20plant.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dol.gov%2Fagencies%2Foalj%2FPUBLIC%2FWHISTLEBLOWER%2FREFERENCES%2FREFERENCE_WORKS%2FAIR21%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20AIR21%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20law%20protecting%20airline%20safety%20whistleblowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarnett's%20lawyer%2C%20Brian%20Knowles%2C%20said%20the%20former%20Boeing%20manager%20was%20supposed%20to%20report%20for%20the%20third%20day%20of%20his%20deposition%20on%20Friday%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.corporatecrimereporter.com%2Fnews%2F200%2Fboeing-whistleblower-found-dead-in-charleston-after-break-in-depositions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECorporate%20Crime%20Reporter.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20questioned%20by%20Boeing's%20lawyers%20on%20Thursday%20and%20then%20cross-examined%20by%20Knowles%20on%20Friday%2C%20but%20didn't%20show%20up%20or%20respond%20to%20calls%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Knowles%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarnett's%20lawyers%20asked%20his%20hotel%20to%20check%20on%20the%20whistleblower%2C%2