to%20being%20touted%20as%20%E2%80%98the%20moment%E2%80%99%20when%20India%20experienced%20a%20%E2%80%98civilisational%20reawakening%E2%80%99%20and%20when%20it%20exited%20its%20%E2%80%98colonial%20mindset%E2%80%99%20culturally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20dangerous%20concentration%20of%20political%20and%20quasi-religious%20power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20show%20of%20unprecedented%20concentration%20of%20political%20power%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20one%20person%20in%20democratic%20India.%20And%20along%20with%20that%20came%20the%20choreographed%20assertion%20that%20Modi%20was%20now%20also%20the%20%E2%80%98high%20priest%E2%80%99%20of%20Hindu%20religion%20and%20culture.%20That%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%20went%20ahead%20despite%20objections%20of%20the%20Shankracharyas%2C%20shows%20that%20Modi%20was%20confident%20of%20taking%20them%20on%2C%20and%20replacing%20them%20in%20public%20perception%20as%20the%20new%20%E2%80%98defender%20of%20the%20faith%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20politics%20and%20religion%2C%20two%20major%20sources%20of%20power%20in%20any%20nation%2C%20more%20so%20in%20India%2C%20are%20now%20alarmingly%20concentrated%20in%20one%20person.%20Possibly%20more%20than%20ever%20before%20in%20modern%20India.%20Others%2C%20with%20whom%20such%20power%20has%20normally%20shared%20in%20a%20robust%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20fellow%20party%20leaders%2C%20ideological%20fountainheads%2C%20opposition%20politicians%2C%20tall%20state%20leaders%2C%20other%20pillars%20of%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20the%20judiciary%2C%20media%2C%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20election%20commission%2C%20and%20even%20religious%20heads%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20are%20all%20possibly%20at%20their%20weakest%20in%20recent%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20hold%20this%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20a%20few%20weeks%20to%20another%20three-day%20mega%20jamboree%2C%20the%20pre-wedding%20celebrations%20of%20Anant%20Ambani%20and%20Radhika%20Merchant%20from%20March%201%20to%203.%20Anant%E2%80%99s%20daddy%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20and%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20richest%20man%2C%20ninth%20richest%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Mukesh%20Ambani%2C%20splurged%20millions%2C%20as%20the%20world%20gawked.%20A%20reported%20USD%207%20million%20fee%20for%20Rihanna%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20event%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20130%20flights%20into%20Jamnagar%20for%20the%20event%2C%20which%20even%20got%20%E2%80%98international%20airport%E2%80%99%20status%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20On%20social%20media%2C%20every%20tiny%20video%20clip%20related%20to%20the%20event%20went%20viral%2C%20exposing%20our%20insatiable%20appetite%20for%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20super-rich%20and%20famous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMukesh%20Bhai%20%E2%80%93%20An%20economic%20superpower%20and%20flaunting%20it%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20event%20was%20not%20just%20about%20the%20Ambanis%20rubbing%20their%20wealth%20in%20our%20faces.%20If%20it%20was%20just%20that%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20remarkable%2C%20because%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20rich%20and%20flashy%2C%20it%20is%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20significantly%2C%20this%20was%20a%20demonstration%20of%20the%20power%20and%20clout%20that%20comes%20with%20this%20wealth.%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20punched%20above%20his%20weight%20in%20the%20list%20of%20the%20richest%2C%20and%20made%20sure%20that%20%234%2C%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20and%20%237%2C%20Bill%20Gates%20made%20it%20to%20the%20event.%20(Aside%20%E2%80%93%20the%20net%20worth%20of%20Mark%2C%20Bill%20and%20Mukesh%2C%20equals%20the%20GDP%20of%20Hungary!)%20Gates%20and%20Zuckerberg%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20paid%20to%20be%20there%2C%20right%3F%20So%20what%20brought%20them%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11214501%2FUntitled-design-34-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11214501%2FUntitled-design-34-1.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11214501%2FUntitled-design-34-1-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11214501%2FUntitled-design-34-1-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701182%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMukesh%20Ambani%20and%20Nita%20Ambani.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20YouTube%20video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20economic%20%E2%80%98power%E2%80%99%20that%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20now%20wields%20%E2%80%93%20the%20size%20of%20Reliance%20Industries%2C%20the%20prospect%20of%20doing%20business%20with%20the%20Ambani%20behemoth%2C%20awareness%20of%20the%20clout%20that%20Mukesh%20bhai%20wields%20in%20the%20corridors%20of%20power%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%20and%20other%20significant%20political%20and%20business%20capitals%20of%20India.%20It%20reveals%20that%20Microsoft%20and%20Facebook%20recognise%20that%20doing%20business%20with%20India%20also%20means%20doing%20business%20with%20Reliance.%20After%20decades%20of%20enjoying%20MFB%20(%E2%80%98Most%20Favoured%20Business%E2%80%99)%20status%2C%20Reliance%20is%20now%20a%20%E2%80%98country-size%E2%80%99%20economic%20entity%20operating%20within%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20today%20enjoys%20unprecedented%20economic%20power%20in%20India.%20While%20a%20few%20other%20business%20houses%20aspire%20to%20match%20him%2C%20Ambani%20is%20clearly%20the%20trailblazer%2C%20certainly%20the%20one%20most%20aware%20of%20his%20accumulated%20power%2C%20also%20prepared%20to%20flaunt%20it%2C%20possibly%20along%20with%20the%20readiness%20to%20wield%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20omnipresent%20Ambani%20%E2%80%98soft%20power%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnAdd%20to%20this%2C%20the%20Ambanis%E2%80%99%20focus%20in%20recent%20years%20on%20building%20their%20%E2%80%98soft%20power%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20muscle%2C%20clout%2C%20and%20visibility.%20Nita%20Ambani%20has%20been%20the%20face%20of%20their%20stakes%20in%20cricket%20and%20football.%20The%20promotional%20campaigns%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20IPL%20franchise%2C%20and%20ISL%2C%20feature%20her%20prominently.%20Her%20presence%20at%20IPL%20auctions%20is%20a%20constant%2C%20as%20well%20as%20her%20presence%20at%20most%20IPL%20matches.%20Jio%20Cinema%20now%20also%20has%20the%20rights%20to%20cover%20all%20cricket%20played%20in%20India%2C%20which%20translates%20into%20many%20more%20crores%20of%20eyeballs%20for%20Reliance%20to%20romance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20remember%20that%20Reliance%20got%20directly%20into%20media%20ownership%20with%20the%20buyout%20of%20Network18%20in%202014.%20And%20just%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20Jamnagar%20jamboree%2C%20Reliance%20announced%20its%20merger%20with%20Disney%E2%80%99s%20India%20assets%20to%20create%20a%20USD%208%20billion%20media%20entity%2C%20the%20largest%20in%20India.%20And%20the%20chairperson%20of%20this%20new%20entity%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Nita%20Ambani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20top%20cricketers%20like%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20an%20uncomplaining%20Mumbai%20Indians%20mascot%20for%2016%20years%2C%20to%20every%20major%20film%20star%20that%20you%20can%20name%2C%20who%20make%20it%20to%20every%20Ambani%20bash%2C%20ready%20to%20break%20into%20dance%20if%20required%2C%20there%20is%20probably%20no%20popular%20cultural%20Indian%20icon%20who%20would%2C%20or%20could%2C%20turn%20down%20an%20Ambani%20invite.%20Jamnagar%20saw%20that%20raw%20Ambani%20clout%20hammered%20home%20yet%20again.%20A%20video%20clip%20shows%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Aamir%20Khan%20dancing%20on%20stage%20together%20at%20the%20pre-wedding.%20Certainly%20rare%2C%20if%20not%20never%20before.%20And%20that%20was%20the%20point%20being%20made%20%E2%80%93%20watch%20this%2C%20and%20understand%20that%20we%2C%20the%20Ambanis%2C%20can%20make%20this%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20is%20this%3F%20It%20is%20a%20never%20before%20concentration%20of%20economic%20power%2C%20and%20soft%20cultural%20power%2C%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20one%20person%2C%20Mukesh%20Ambani.%20In%20a%20country%20where%20%E2%80%98cronyism%E2%80%99%20is%20rife%2C%20where%20corruption%20at%20every%20level%20is%20a%20well-documented%20reality%2C%20such%20economic%20power%20is%20monopolised%2C%20to%20a%20substantial%20extent%2C%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20aspirations%20of%20several%20other%20entrepreneurs.%20Which%20makes%20it%20unhealthy%2C%20and%20simply%20wrong%20and%20undemocratic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20add%20massive%20soft%20power%20to%20it%2C%20from%20entertainment%20to%20sports%20to%20news%20media%2C%20it%20becomes%20easier%20to%20control%20perceptions%2C%20and%20to%20keep%20the%20Ambani%20reputation%20squeaky%20clean%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20again%2C%20hold%20this%20thought%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAn%20%E2%80%98entitled%E2%80%99%20political%20opposition%20is%20no%20opposition%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20finally%20also%20look%20at%20the%20reality%20of%20%E2%80%98entitlement%E2%80%99%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20many%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20elite%20and%20upper-crust%20believe%20they%20are%20%E2%80%98entitled%E2%80%99%20to%20all%20that%20they%20have.%20But%20%E2%80%98entitlement%E2%80%99%20is%20playing%20out%20most%20damagingly%20among%20those%20who%20should%20be%20challenging%20the%20political%20power%20of%20Modi%2C%20who%20should%20be%20espousing%20an%20idea%20of%20India%20that%20can%20counter%20this%20clearly%20%E2%80%98un-democratic%E2%80%99%20concentration%20of%20political%2C%20economic%2C%20religious%20and%20cultural%20power%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20very%20few%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F22162521%2FIMG_1705.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F22162521%2FIMG_1705.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F22162521%2FIMG_1705-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F22162521%2FIMG_1705-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637196%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20who%20are%20these%20politicians%3F%20Look%20at%20all%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20dynasty%20driven%20opposition%20political%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%2C%20DMK%2C%20NCP%2C%20SP%2C%20RJD%2C%20BRS%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20%E2%80%93%20to%20name%20the%20prominent%20ones.%20Or%20even%20parties%20run%20by%20leaders%20who%20cannot%20be%20challenged%2C%20such%20as%20TMC%2C%20BJD%2C%20or%20even%20the%20moribund%20BSP.%20The%20leaders%20and%20%E2%80%98political%20families%E2%80%99%20running%20these%20parties%20are%20showing%20no%20readiness%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20their%20%E2%80%98entitlements%E2%80%99.%20They%20are%20showing%20no%20readiness%20to%20transform%20their%20parties%20into%20transparent%2C%20merit-based%20organisations.%20And%20so%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20they%20are%20in%20no%20moral%20position%20to%20critique%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20self-centered%20brand%20of%20politics%20or%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20unabashed%20demonstrations%20of%20money%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20where%20does%20that%20leave%20us%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJust%20before%202024%20elections%2C%20people%E2%80%99s%20power%20is%20Struggling%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20a%20democracy%2C%20we%20now%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20a%20vast%2C%20disproportionate%20amount%20of%20political%20power%20is%20concentrated%20in%20one%20man.%20Many%20among%20us%20have%20even%20accepted%20him%20as%20the%20sole%20%E2%80%98keeper%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98defender%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Hindu%20faith%2C%20making%20him%20all-powerful.%20And%20at%20what%20cost%20has%20this%20happened%3F%20At%20the%20cost%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20a%20democracy%2C%20in%20which%20equal%20opportunity%20is%20a%20core%20value%2C%20we%20have%20watched%20incredible%20economic%20power%20pour%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20one%20individual%2C%20with%20a%20few%20more%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98super-rich%E2%80%99%20aspiring%20to%20join%20this%20very%20exclusive%20power%20club.%20At%20what%20cost%3F%20Again%2C%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20a%20democracy%2C%20our%20%E2%80%98entitled%E2%80%99%20political%20class%2C%20from%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20is%20inherently%20incapable%20of%20resisting%20this%20onslaught%20of%20authoritarianism%20or%20espousing%20the%20cause%20of%20a%20more%20economically%20equitable%20India.%20And%20so%2C%20they%20cannot%20stop%2C%20let%20alone%20reverse%20this%20process%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20rapidly%20depleting%20people%E2%80%99s%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20move%20towards%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20we%20must%20at%20least%20understand%20what%E2%80%99s%20in%20play%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20at%20stake%2C%20and%20what%20may%20well%20be%20in%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710210545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F01124234%2F4DEA30F3-B40A-474E-AC92-B2062CD0D966.png%22%2C%2