ms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108416728.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-calls-tiktok-a-threat-but-says-some-kids-could-go-crazy-without-it%2Farticleshow%2F108416728.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-calls-tiktok-a-threat-but-says-some-kids-could-go-crazy-without-it%2Famp_articleshow%2F108416728.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-calls-tiktok-a-threat-but-says-some-kids-could-go-crazy-without-it%2Famp_articleshow%2F108416728.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20have%20an%20invisible%20disability.%20Flying%20is%20extra%20stressful%2C%20and%20other%20travelers%20don't%20understand%20why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mother%20and%20daughter%20on%20flight%20wearing%20facemasks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e6d3a56080194819fc7207%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrea%20McKenna%20Brankin%20has%20bipolar%20disorder%20so%20faces%20another%20layer%20of%20stress%20when%20travelng.%3Cp%3EAndrea%20McKenna%20Brankin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndrea%20McKenna%20Brankin%20is%20an%20American%20mom%20who%20lives%20in%20Singapore%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20daughter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20has%20bipolar%20disorder%20and%20finds%20traveling%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Asia%20stressful.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELavender%20oil%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20Harry%20Potter%20have%20all%20helped%20her%20reduce%20stress%20while%20traveling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20and%20lines%20were%20building%20up%20at%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20jetway.%20There%20had%20already%20been%20several%20delays%20and%20I%20was%20getting%20nervous.%20Would%20I%20miss%20my%20connection%3F%20Would%20there%20be%20enough%20overhead%20space%20for%20my%20bags%3F%20Will%20they%20serve%20water%3F%20These%20questions%20vexed%20me%20for%20what%20felt%20like%20an%20eternity%20until%20I%20finally%20heard%20the%20announcement%20that%20we'd%20be%20boarding%20soon.%20When%20the%20airline%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famid-airline-chaos-wheelchair-users-are-the-latest-casualties-delays-cancellations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboarding%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief.%20Although%20the%20check-in%20person%20looking%20at%20me%20questioningly%20%E2%80%94%20my%20disability%20is%20invisible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20can%20be%20stressful%20for%20everyone%2C%20but%20even%20more%20so%20for%20me%2C%20as%20I%20have%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-with-bipolar-and-ptsd-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20bipolar%20disorder%3C%2Fa%3E.%20External%20stressors%20like%20delays%20and%20even%20snarky%20passengers%20make%20dealing%20with%20the%20condition%20much%20harder.%20But%20it's%20something%20I've%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20manage%2C%20especially%20after%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20moved%20from%20Chicago%20to%20Singapore%2012%20years%20ago.%20I%20travel%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Asia%20at%20least%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20along%20with%20regional%20travel%20in%20both%20the%20States%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%20These%20flights%20range%20between%2090%20minutes%20to%20almost%2020%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fbipolar-symptoms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBipolar%20is%20a%20mood%20disorder%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20affects%20more%20than%2040%20million%20people%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fdetail%2Fmental-disorders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Health%20Organization%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20condition%20is%20characterized%20by%20extreme%20mood%20swings%20between%20depression%20and%20mania%20and%20can%20affect%20behavior%2C%20especially%20in%20high-stress%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20take%20a%20variety%20of%20medications%20to%20keep%20these%20swings%20and%20symptoms%20%E2%80%94%20like%20high%20anxiety%20and%20paranoia%20%E2%80%94%20at%20bay.%20I%20need%20the%20meds%20every%20day%2C%20so%20it's%20always%20the%20first%20thing%20on%20my%20packing%20list.%20This%20presents%20the%20first%20of%20several%20challenges%20I've%20unpacked%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20avoid%20medication%20mishaps%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Multiple%20days%20of%20the%20week%20pill%20dispensers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e6de416080194819fc7253%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe%20packs%20at%20enough%20medication%20for%20at%20least%202%20extra%20weeks.%3Cp%3EAndrea%20McKenna%20Brankin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20travel%2C%20I%20have%20to%20carry%20enough%20medication%20to%20last%20the%20whole%20trip%2C%20plus%20extra%20in%20case%20of%20delays.%20Many%20of%20my%20trips%20are%20long%2C%20especially%20the%20ones%20to%20the%20US%2C%20so%20it%20can%20take%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space.%20Whether%20short%20or%20long%2C%20it's%20important%20for%20me%20to%20carry%20a%20letter%20for%20customs%2C%20written%20and%20signed%20by%20my%20psychiatrist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20describes%20what%20my%20medications%20are%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20the%20doses%20and%20why%20I%20take%20them%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20event%20that%20I%20get%20stopped.%20This%20is%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fketamine-therapy-depression-treatment-addictive-drug-clinics-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emood-altering%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20called%20psychotropics%20%E2%80%94%20are%20noted%20as%20illegal%20without%20a%20prescription.%20Many%20countries%2C%20including%20Singapore%20and%20the%20US%2C%20have%20strict%20laws%20on%20carrying%20this%20kind%20of%20medication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20managed%20to%20plan%20ahead%20the%20best%20way%20I%20can%2C%20always%20packing%20the%20letter%20in%20my%20carry-on%2C%20carrying%20enough%20meds%20for%20at%20least%20two%20extra%20weeks%2C%20and%20having%20a%20doctor%20on%20call%20in%20case%20I%20need%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBeing%20bipolar%20and%20a%20mom%20adds%20another%20layer%20of%20stress%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mother%20and%20daughter%20wearing%20matching%20outfits%20at%20the%20airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e6dd676080194819fc723e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMother%20and%20daughter%20dressed%20up%20in%20matching%20travel%20outfits.%3Cp%3EAndrea%20McKenna%20Brankin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-with-kids-major-mistakes-best-tips-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETraveling%20with%20children%20is%20stressful%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Full%20stop.%20Other%20travelers%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20around%20you%20in%20case%20of%20crying%2C%20airline%20staff%20get%20fed%20up%20with%20having%20to%20do%20more%20for%20you%2C%20and%20you%20yourself%20don't%20get%20much%20rest%20at%20all.%20These%20challenges%20are%20exponential%20with%20bipolar%20disorder%20because%20stress%2C%20especially%20with%20other%20people%2C%20is%20a%20real%20trigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20more%20than%20one%20occasion%2C%20I've%20been%20treated%20poorly%20as%20a%20traveling%20mom.%20The%20most%20unbelievable%20was%20when%20a%20flight%20attendant%20handed%20me%20a%20large%20garbage%20bag%20and%20told%20me%20it%20was%20for%20my%20baby's%20diapers.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20have%20to%20keep%20the%20diapers%20at%20my%20seat%20in%20this%20bag%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked.%20She%20explained%20that%20leaving%20diapers%20in%20the%20bathroom%20bothered%20other%20passengers.%20I%20was%20seated%20in%20business%20class%20when%20this%20happened%20and%20handed%20the%20bag%20back%20to%20her%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTalk%20to%20my%20husband%20about%20it.%20He%20paid%20for%20the%20business%20class%20tickets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20manage%20this%20part%20of%20flying%20by%20being%20very%20prepared%20as%20a%20mom%2C%20with%20supplies%20like%20extra%20diapers%2C%20toys%2C%20headphones%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20clothes.%20One%20nightmare%20flight%20had%20me%20tending%20to%20my%20daughter%20every%2010%20minutes%20for%2014%20hours.%20But%20as%20my%20kid%20grows%20up%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20nearly%2012%20%E2%80%94%20traveling%20is%20getting%20easier.%20Just%20her%20being%20able%20to%20operate%20her%20own%20devices%20and%20seat%20TV%20was%20a%20game%20changer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20prepared%20for%20the%20trips%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-a-mom-with-bipolar-disorder-the-stigma-is-huge-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebipolar%20disorder%3C%2Fa%3E%20means%20eating%20well%20and%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20rest%20and%20exercise%20before%20the%20trip.%20The%20body%20releases%20endorphins%20when%20you%20exercise%2C%20and%20it's%20also%20been%20said%20to%20combat%20stress%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fbipolar-disorder%2Fexercise%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHealthline%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20also%20make%20sure%20my%20meds%20and%20symptoms%20are%20in%20order.%20I%20bring%20lavender%20oil%20for%20inhaling%20as%20well%20as%20lots%20of%20skincare%20products%20to%20do%20some%20self-care%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EQuality%20time%20with%20the%20family%20makes%20it%20worth%20all%20the%20hassle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20holding%20a%20beer%20with%20woman%20and%20young%20girl%2C%20with%20palm%20trees%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7de7890413ab8e1d9935e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETraveling%20with%20bipolar%20disorder%20is%20stressful%2C%20but%20spending%20time%20with%20her%20family%20makes%20it%20worth%20it.%3Cp%3EAndrea%20McKenna%20Brankin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20overall%20challenges%20of%20traveling%20with%20bipolar%20disorder%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjet-lag-mental-illness-treatment-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejet%20lag%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20screws%20up%20your%20biorhythms%2C%20sleep%2C%20eating%2C%20and%20meds%20schedule.%20As%20my%20prescription%20includes%20day%20and%20night%20medication%2C%20it%20took%20me%20a%20while%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20and%20when%20to%20take%20each%20when%20I%20was%20crossing%20the%20international%20date%20line.%20I%20now%20focus%20on%20taking%20the%20night%20meds%20and%20sometimes%20double%20up%20on%20the%20mood%20stabilizers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20use%20sleeping%20pills%2C%20but%20I%20do%20take%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2Fmelatonin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emelatonin%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20days%20before%20a%20long%20flight%20and%20continue%20for%20as%20long%20as%20needed%20once%20I%20arrive.%20My%20family%20has%20tried%20all%20different%20flight%20times%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20from%20arriving%20at%20dawn%20to%20arriving%20at%209%20p.m.%20to%20see%20which%20works%20better.%20Honestly%2C%20no%20time%20is%20perfect.%20But%20if%20I%20take%20good%20care%20of%20myself%20before%20the%20trip%2C%20I'm%20usually%20in%20a%20good%20place%20mentally%20and%20physically%20to%20start%20my%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20I%20can%20sleep%20or%20not%2C%20I%20rely%20heavily%20on%20distractions.%20I%20can't%20manage%20to%20read%20books%2C%20but%20I%20do%20watch%20movies%2C%20specifically%20Harry%20Potter.%20Downloaded%20on%20my%20phone%20or%20on%20the%20seat%20TV%2C%20the%20Harry%20Potter%20series%20includes%20seven%20films%20with%20more%20than%2015%20hours%20of%20viewing%20time.%20That%20almost%20gets%20me%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Singapore%20to%20San%20Francisco.%20Mischief%20managed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20bipolar%20disorder%20always%20presents%20daily%20challenges%20whether%20I'm%20in%20the%20air%20or%20on%20the%20ground.%20But%20I%20think%20I'm%20handling%20it%20pretty%20well.%20The%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20to%20be%20with%20my%20family%2C%20and%20that's%20always%20worth%20the%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20personal%20essay%20about%20living%20abroad%20or%20parenting%20that%20you%20want%20to%20share%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20editor%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aakarplus%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eakarplus%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-with-disability-bipolar-disorder-travel-abroad-stress-medication-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710203221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7f5596080194819fce76b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-with-disability-bipolar-disorder-travel-abroad-stress-medication-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20frequent%20traveler%20with%20bipolar%20disorder