y%20Kimmel%20and%20John%20Cena%20onstage%20at%20the%202024%20Oscars%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ef6fb0ce7f1785b2e89f4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJimmy%20Kimmel%20and%20John%20Cena%20onstage%20at%20the%202024%20Oscars%2C%20which%20didn't%20get%20great%20ratings.%3Cp%3EFrank%20Micelotta%2FDisney%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Hollywood%20and%20the%20TV%20industry%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20revive%20the%20audience%20for%20the%20Oscars%2C%20which%20has%20been%20plummeting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjon-stewart-daily-show-audience-old-small-tv-ratings-streaming-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealongside%20the%20rest%20of%20conventional%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20last%20big%20hope%3A%20That%20if%20the%20awards%20featured%20big%20movies%20people%20have%20seen%20or%20at%20least%20heard%20of%2C%20audiences%20might%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20supposed%20to%20happen%20this%20year%2C%20when%20monster%20hits%20%26quot%3BBarbie%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BOppenheimer%26quot%3B%20were%20both%20up%20for%20multiple%20awards%2C%20including%20Best%20Picture.%20And%20the%20producers%20for%20ABC's%20broadcast%20smartly%20leaned%20into%20it%2C%20by%20doing%20things%20like%20bringing%20in%20%26quot%3BBarbie%26quot%3B%20nominee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslate.com%2Fculture%2F2024%2F03%2Fryan-gosling-oscars-im-just-ken-performance-barbie-slash.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERyan%20Gosling%20to%20sing%20and%20dance%2C%20to%20general%20acclaim%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%E2%80%A6%20we%20have%20a%20real%20glass%20half-empty%2Fhalf-full%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20per%20ABC%2C%20Sunday%20night's%20show%20drew%2019.5%20million%20viewers%2C%20which%20ABC%20notes%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Ba%204-year%20high%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20third%20year%20in%20a%20row%20that%20the%20audience%20has%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20that's%20good%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%3A%20That%20means%20this%20year's%20telecast%20still%20drew%20considerably%20less%20than%20the%2023.6%20million%20viewers%20who%20watched%20the%202020%20show%2C%20which%20didn't%20have%20anything%20like%20%26quot%3BBarbie%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BOppenheimer%2C%26quot%3B%20box-office-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oscars.org%2Foscars%2Fceremonies%2F2020%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBest%20Picture%3C%2Fa%3E%20nominees%20were%20ones%20regular%20folks%20may%20have%20seen%20in%20theaters%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BFord%20V.%20Ferrari%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BJoker.%26quot%3B%20And%20the%20big%20winner%20that%20night%20was%20%26quot%3BParasite%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Korean-made%20slasher%2Fsatire%2C%20which%20brought%20in%20about%20%24260%20million%20in%20worldwide%20box%20office%20%E2%80%94%20really%20big%20for%20a%20Korean-language%20film%2C%20but%20not%20a%20juggernaut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%3A%20If%20this%20year's%20numbers%2C%20bolstered%20by%20giant%20hits%2C%20are%20a%20win%20for%20the%20Oscars%20%E2%80%A6%20maybe%20we%20have%20to%20accept%20the%20fact%20that%20Oscars%20are%20never%20coming%20anywhere%20close%20to%20all%20the%20way%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20context%3A%20As%20recently%20as%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Elot%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20people%20watched%20the%20Oscars%3A%20Nearly%2044%20million%20tuned%20in%20to%20watch%20the%202014%20show%2C%20where%20the%20Best%20Picture%20award%20went%20to%20%26quot%3B12%20Years%20a%20Slave%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20good%20movie%2C%20but%20definitely%20not%20a%20crowd-pleaser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20was%20back%20when%20TV%20boosters%20had%20hoped%20that%20Oscar%20broadcasts%2C%20which%20are%20live%20and%20sometimes%20unpredictable%2C%20would%20be%20immune%20to%20the%20forces%20shrinking%20conventional%20TV.%20But%20that%20hasn't%20been%20the%20case%3A%20Since%20then%2C%20audiences%20have%20been%20plummeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20reached%20a%20nadir%20in%202021%2C%20when%20COVID%20kept%20people%20out%20of%20movie%20theaters%20and%20forced%20the%20show's%20producers%20to%20film%20the%20show%20in%20a%20train%20station%20instead%20of%20a%20theater%3A%20That%20show%20barely%20cleared%2010%20million%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20show%20has%20rebounded.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20awards%20brought%20in%2018.8%20million%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20hunch%3A%20This%20is%2C%20at%20best%2C%20the%20new%20normal.%20Some%20people%20still%20like%20movies%2C%20and%20some%20people%20still%20like%20seeing%20live%20award%20shows%20about%20movies.%20But%20we're%20never%20going%20back%20to%20the%20old%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbie-oppenheimer-oscars-tv-audience-ratings-jimmy-kimmel-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710200947000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ef95bb90413ab8e1db9f58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbie-oppenheimer-oscars-tv-audience-ratings-jimmy-kimmel-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Oscars%20were%20hoping%20huge%20movies%20would%20generate%20a%20big%20audience.%20Not%20really.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A294%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbie-oppenheimer-oscars-tv-audience-ratings-jimmy-kimmel-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thailand%20Planning%20Film%20Development%20Measures%20and%20%24200%20Million%20Funding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710200700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fva