entary%20elections%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20announced%20a%20ticket%20to%20B.B.%20Patil%2C%20the%20sitting%20BRS%20MP%20from%20Zaheerabad%2C%20overnight%20after%20the%20BRS%20had%20confirmed%20his%20candidature%20from%20the%20same%20constituency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20soon%20as%20he%20resigned%20from%20the%20primary%20membership%20of%20the%20BRS%2C%20the%20BJP%20rolled%20out%20the%20red%20carpet%20for%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20same%20way%2C%20the%20BJP%20announced%20the%20candidature%20of%20Bharat%20Prasad%20from%20the%20Nagarkurnool%20(SC%20reserved)%20constituency%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20of%20his%20father%20and%20sitting%20MP%20from%20the%20constituency%20P.%20Ramulu%20tendering%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamulu%20was%20keen%20on%20handing%20over%20the%20mantle%20to%20his%20son.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20two%20former%20MPs%20of%20the%20BRS%2C%20Ajmeera%20Sitaram%20Naik%20(Mahbubabad)%20and%20Godam%20Nagesh%20(Adilabad)%2C%20and%20two%20former%20MLAs%2C%20Jalagam%20Venkat%20Rao%20(Kothagudem)%20and%20S.%20Saidi%20Reddy%20(Huzurnagar)%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EG.%20Srinivas%2C%20a%20BRS%20candidate%20who%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%20from%20Peddapalli%20in%202009%2C%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20them%20were%20likely%20to%20get%20tickets%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20defections%20by%20BRS%20leaders%20had%20rattled%20its%20leadership%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20party%20was%20having%20a%20tough%20time%20finding%20strong%20candidates%20to%20contest%20the%20coming%20elections%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20its%20defeat%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20three%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22In%20Telangana%2C%20Five%20Trends%20Highlight%20Divides%2C%20Gains%2C%20Losses%20and%20Blows%20to%20Expansion%20Plans%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bharat-rashtra-samithi-congress-kcr%5C%22%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20Five%20Trends%20Highlight%20Divides%2C%20Gains%2C%20Losses%20and%20Blows%20to%20Expansion%20Plans%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20leaders%20like%20former%20minister%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20swung%20into%20action%20and%20contacted%20former%20BRS%20MLA%20Aroori%20Ramesh%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20convince%20him%20after%20he%20threatened%20to%20walk%20out%20and%20contest%20from%20Warangal%20(SC%20reserved)%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERao%20also%20called%20up%20half%20a%20dozen%20corporators%20of%20the%20Warangal%20municipal%20corporation%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20switching%20over%20to%20the%20Congress%20when%20they%20had%20declared%20their%20intentions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20lower%20level%2C%20the%20BRS%20leaders%20who%20had%20no%20stakes%20in%20the%20elections%20went%20with%20the%20wind%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20engineered%20the%20defections%2C%20mainly%20targeting%20BRS%20leaders%20who%20are%20potential%20election%20material.%20The%20party%20has%20four%20MPs%20and%20hopes%20to%20add%20two%20more%20to%20the%20tally%20realistically%2C%20though%20on%20record%2C%20its%20leaders%20claimed%20they%20targeted%20winning%20ten%20out%20of%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20state%20secretary%20S.%20Prakash%20Reddy%20said%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20goal%20was%20to%20overtake%20the%20BRS%20in%20terms%20of%20numbers%20to%20take%20the%20second%20spot%20behind%20the%20ruling%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20will%20stand%20the%20BJP%20in%20good%20stead%20to%20assume%20power%20in%20the%202028%20assembly%20elections%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20idea%20was%20to%20erase%20the%20BRS%20from%20the%20political%20spectrum%20by%202028.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20BRS%20leader%20and%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20state%20planning%20board%20B.%20Vinod%20Kumar%20admitted%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdevour%E2%80%9D%20the%20BRS.%20He%20said%20the%20BJP%20was%20playing%20the%20snake-and-ladder%20game%20but%20warned%20that%20the%20BRS%20will%20climb%20up%20the%20ladder%20again%20if%20it%20went%20down.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVinod%20Kumar%20said%20that%20half%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidates%2C%20including%20its%20well%20known%20faces%20like%20former%20minister%20Eatala%20Rajender%2C%20were%20from%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20eight%20assembly%20seats%20recently%2C%20up%20from%20just%20one%20in%20the%202018%20polls%2C%20and%20also%20improved%20its%20vote%20share%20from%207%25%20to%2014%25%20during%20the%20five-year%20period.%20The%20party%20aims%20to%20consolidate%20on%20these%20gains%20with%20an%20improved%20performance%20in%20the%20coming%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bjp-brs-and-the-truth-behind-the-conspiracy-theories%5C%22%3ETelangana%2C%20BJP%2C%20BRS%20and%20the%20Truth%20Behind%20the%20Conspiracy%20Theories%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20B.B.%20Patil%20and%20Bharat%20Prasad%2C%20others%20whose%20candidature%20was%20announced%20previously%20are%20Union%20tourism%20minister%20G.%20Kishan%20Reddy%20(Secunderabad)%2C%20D.%20Arvind%20(Nizamabad)%20and%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20(Karimnagar)%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20are%20sitting%20MPs%3B%20as%20well%20as%20Madhavi%20Latha%20(Hyderabad)%2C%20Konda%20Vishweshwar%20Reddy%20(Chevella)%2C%20Boora%20Narsaiah%20Goud%20(Bhongir)%20and%20Eatala%20Rajender%20(Malkajgiri).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20latest%20entrants%2C%20ex-MPs%20Sitaram%20Naik%20and%20Godam%20Nagesh%20were%20tipped%20to%20retain%20their%20constituencies%2C%20Mahbubabad%20and%20Adilabad%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Jalagam%20Venkat%20Rao%20expected%20a%20ticket%20from%20Khammam%2C%20Saidi%20Reddy%20from%20Nalgonda%20and%20G.%20Srinivas%20from%20Peddapalli.%20That%20leaves%20decision-making%20to%20be%20completed%20for%20Warangal%2C%20Medak%20and%20Mahbubnagar%2C%20where%20there%20is%20stiff%20competition%20for%20selection%20between%20former%20minister%20D.K.%20Aruna%20and%20ex-MP%20A.P.%20Jitender%20Reddy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20BJP%20discard%20and%20noted%20educationist%20Malka%20Komaraiah%20has%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20BRS%20as%20a%20potential%20contestant%20from%20Malkajgiri%2C%20where%20the%20former%20party%20has%20fielded%20Eatala%20Rajender.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20so%20far%20announced%20only%20five%20candidates%20amidst%20the%20spate%20of%20desertions%20and%20unwillingness%20of%20some%20of%20its%20leaders%20to%20enter%20the%20poll%20fray.%20Among%20the%20latter%20are%20the%20sitting%20MP%20of%20Chevella%20G.%20Ranjeet%20Reddy%20and%20strongman%20C.%20Malla%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20son%20Bhadra%20Reddy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20had%20recently%20pulled%20down%20a%20college%20building%20and%20road%20infrastructure%20constructed%20by%20Malla%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20son-in-law%20and%20MLA%2C%20Rajasekhar%20Reddy%2C%20for%20various%20permissions%20violations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOtherwise%2C%20Malla%20Reddy%2C%20a%20former%20minister%20who%20runs%20a%20chain%20of%20professional%20colleges%20as%20well%20as%20a%20huge%20health%20city%2C%20made%20a%20strong%20pitch%20for%20his%20son%20Bhadra%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20BRS%20from%20Malkajgiri.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11203737%2FMalha-Reddy-1024x461.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11203737%2FMalha-Reddy-1024x461.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11203737%2FMalha-Reddy-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11203737%2FMalha-Reddy.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701168%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22378%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMalla%20Reddy%20is%20a%20two-time%20Telangana%20MLA%20and%20was%20also%20MP%20from%20its%20Malkajgiri%20seat.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40chmallareddyMLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20demolition%2C%20Malla%20Reddy%20rushed%20to%20the%20government%20with%20a%20request%20to%20join%20the%20Congress.%20He%20assured%20Congress%20leaders%20that%20he%20would%20mobilise%20a%20crowd%20of%20one%20lakh%20for%20his%20joining%20ceremony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20sitting%20MP%20P.%20Ramulu%20quit%20the%20BRS%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20as%20his%20request%20for%20the%20elevation%20of%20his%20son%20Bharat%20Prasad%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20Nagarkurnool%20zilla%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eparishad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20turned%20down%20by%20BRS%20president%20and%20former%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamulu%20and%20Patil%E2%80%99s%20resignations%20from%20the%20BRS%20had%20a%20deep%20impact%20on%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20as%20the%20two%20constituencies%20were%20considered%20strong%20bets%20for%20it%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20accommodated%20Bharat%20Prasad%20in%20Nagarkurnool%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Shruti%2C%20daughter%20of%20former%20party%20president%20Bangaru%20Laxman%2C%20who%20was%20its%20candidate%20in%20the%20last%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20election%20from%20Nagarkurnool%20has%20assumed%20significance%20this%20time%20following%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP).%20The%20BRS%20has%20conceded%20the%20seat%20to%20BSP%20state%20president%20and%20former%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20officer%20R.S.%20Praveen%20Kumar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20leaving%20the%20seat%20to%20the%20BSP%20and%20announcing%20candidates%20in%20five%20other%20constituencies%2C%20the%20BRS%20is%20waiting%20for%20rival%20parties%20to%20release%20their%20lists%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20discards%20coming%20its%20way%20to%20join%20the%20battle%20lines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BRS%20candidates%20so%20far%20are%20B.%20Vinod%20Kumar%20(Karimnagar)%3B%20sitting%20MPs%20Nama%20Nageswara%C2%A0%20Rao%20(Khammam)%2C%20M.%20Kavitha%20(Mahbubabad)%20and%20M.%20Srinivas%20Reddy%20(Mahbubnagar)%3B%20and%20former%20minister%20Koppula%20Easwar%20(Peddapalli).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20sitting%20MP%2C%20N.%20Venkatesh%20(Peddapalli)%2C%20joined%20the%20Congress%20earlier%20but%20has%20not%20figured%20in%20the%20first%20list%20of%20four%20candidates%20released%20by%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChandrashekar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20Kavitha%2C%20who%20had%20lost%20the%20previous%20election%20from%20Nizamabad%2C%20is%20a%20doubtful%20starter%20as%20the%20family%20had%20reportedly%20decided%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20fielding%20her%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710173730000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11202507%2FDefectors-II.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-telangana-brs-suffers-another-setback-as-bjp-engineers-defections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20improved%20its%20vote%20share%20from%207%25%20to%2014%25%20between%20the%202018%20and%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Telangana's%20BJP%20aims%20to%20consolidate%20on%20these%20gains%20with%20an%20improved%20performance%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-telangana-brs-suffers-another-setback-as-bjp-engineers-defections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20warns%20against%20all%20travel%20to%20Caribbean%20nation%20as%20gang%20violence%20rages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710172740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-haiti-port-au-prince_6487173.jpg%3F20240311164936%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhaiti-gang-violence-uk-warns-against-all-travel-to-caribbean-nation-as-us-secretary-of-state-tries-to-solve-crisis-13092737%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK%20government%20has%20warned%20against%20all%20travel%20to%20Haiti%20as%20intense%20fighting%20and%20gang%20violence%20continues%20to%20spiral%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20nation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhaiti-gang-violence-uk-warns-against-all-travel-to-caribbean-nation-as-us-secretary-of-state-tries-to-solve-crisis-13092737%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhaiti-gang-violence-uk-warns-against-all-travel-to-caribbean-nation-as-us-secretary-of-state-tries-to-solve-crisis-13092737%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhaiti-gang-violence-uk-warns-against-all-travel-to-caribbean-nation-as-us-secretary-of-state-tries-to-solve-crisis-13092737%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unlike%20Mamata%2C%20Lalu%20Never%20Showed%20Signs%20of%20Bending%20In%20Front%20Of%20Saffron%20Forces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11204317%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-11-at-8.40.52-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-bjp-will-suffer-its-bigger-ever-defeat-in-2024-says-lalu-prasad-yadav%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20this%20author%2C%20former%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20had%20predicted%20the%20%E2%80%9Cworst-ever%20defeat%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20exuded%20confidence%20that%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20desert%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20president%E2%80%99s%C2%A0prophecy%20about%20his%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20counterpart%20and%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20has%20fallen%20on%20its%20face%20with%20the%20latter%20going%20solo%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state.%20It%E2%80%99s%20to%20be%20seen%20to%20what%20extent%20his%20prediction%20regarding%20the%20BJP%20comes%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20was%20a%20founder%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20was%20quite%20loquacious%2C%20at%20least%2C%20in%20her%20words%20against%20the%20Hindutva%20party.%20But%20her%20move%2C%20according%20to%20political%20pundits%2C%20has%20decidedly%20helped%20the%20BJP%20in%20breaking%20the%20larger%20opposition%20unity%20on%20the%20Bengal%20turf.%20The%20eastern%20state%20now%20is%20all%20set%20to%20witness%20a%20triangular%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%2C%20TMC%20and%20the%20Congress-Left%20to%20an%20obvious%20advantage%20of%20the%20party%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20chief%20landed%20in%20Patna%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20first%20oppositions%E2%80%99%20meet%20on%20June%2023%2C%202023%2C%20went%20straight%20to%20Yadav%20and%20bowed%20before%20him.%20The%20picture%20of%20Yadav%20tapping%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20head%20in%20a%20display%20of%20affection%20and%20the%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20describing%20Yadav%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Chighly%20respected%20senior%20pro%E2%80%9D%20fuelled%20a%20perception%20among%20the%20beleaguered%20opposition%20leaders%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfiery%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EDidi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sister)%20and%20%E2%80%9Cindomitable%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20together%20would%20effectively%20challenge%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20perception%20stands%20demolished%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhary%20is%20quoted%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Findia-bloc-collapse-west-bengal-adhir-ranjan-chowdhury-mamata-banerjee-9206712%2F%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20(Banerjee)%20thinks%20the%20Central%20government%20would%20send%20ED%2C%20CBI%E2%80%A6after%20the%20TMC%E2%80%A6%20So%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20alliance%20and%20send%20a%20message%20to%20the%20PMO%20that%20she%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%E2%80%A6and%20that%20she%20is%20not%20fighting%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20measure%20the%20truth%20of%20Choudhary%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20but%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20and%20several%20of%20her%20party%20leaders%20are%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20and%20many%20of%20her%20former%20party%20colleagues%20including%20Shubhendu%20Adhikari%20have%20shifted%20to%20the%20BJP%20to%20%E2%80%9Csave%20their%20skin%E2%80%9D%20in%20corruption%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frjds-jan-vishwas-patna-rally-turns-into-a-big-india-push-first-in-hindi-belt-in-2024%5C%22%3ERJD%E2%80%99s%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Patna%20Rally%20Turns%20Into%20a%20Big%20INDIA%20Push%2C%20First%20in%20Hindi%20Belt%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20former%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20judge%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20joining%20the%20BJP%20is%20being%20linked%20to%20his%20orders%20against%20TMC%20leaders%20in%20cases%20of%20corruption%20which%20he%20had%20passed%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20a%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20are%20different%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20comes%20the%20difference%20between%20Yadav%20and%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agencies%20have%20been%20relentless%20against%20the%20RJD%20president%20and%20his%20family%20members%20for%20years.%20He%20stayed%20in%20jail%20for%20four%20years%20with%20the%20CBI%20ferociously%20opposing%20his%20bail%20from%20the%20lower%20court%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigating%20agencies%E2%80%99%20heat%20on%20him%20and%20his%20family%20members%20increased%20manifold%20with%20Modi%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202014.%20The%20CBI%20dug%20the%20cases%20related%20to%20his%20tenures%20as%20the%20railway%20minister%20(2004-2009)%20which%20it%20had%20closed%20in%202011%20and%20framed%20his%20son%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20wife%20Rabri%20Devi%20and%20their%20daughters%20in%20corruption%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20no%20point%20of%20time%2C%20Yadav%20ever%20gave%20the%20slightest%20hint%20to%20play%20ball%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Rather%2C%20the%20