0%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1767169607943471197%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyadavakhilesh%2Fstatus%2F1767177503955898786%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20are%20forced%20to%20go%20out%20for%20livelihood%2C%20then%20what%20will%20happen%20by%20bringing%20%E2%80%98citizenship%20law%E2%80%99%20for%20others%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20announcement%2C%20Assam%20Jatiya%20Parishad%20president%20Lurinjyoti%20Gogoi%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20day%20for%20Assam%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20Assamese%20people%20to%20fight%20the%20Act%E2%80%99s%20implementation%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Gogoi%2C%20former%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20All%20Assam%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%2C%20said%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20Act%20will%20crush%20the%20identity%2C%20land%20and%20cultural%20rights%20of%20the%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20seeking%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20Assamese%20community%20to%20protect%20their%20rights%20but%20ending%20up%20giving%20it%20the%20biggest%20blow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20from%20Assam%20like%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal%20and%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20failed%20to%20convince%20their%20central%20government%20to%20keep%20Assam%20out%20of%20the%20CAA%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20is%20a%20black%20day%20for%20Assam%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20urge%20people%20to%20get%20ready%20to%20fight%20this%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAct%20still%20sub-judice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20legal%20validity%20of%20the%20CAA%20are%20pending%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20the%20Union%20government%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-caa-hearing-mha-affidavit%5C%22%3Esubmitted%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20defending%20the%20law%20and%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbenign%20piece%20of%20legislation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20prominent%20lawyers%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20CAA%E2%80%99s%20implementation%20was%20a%20sub-judice%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Sanjay%20Hegde%2C%20who%20served%20as%20court-appointed%20interlocutor%20during%20protests%20against%20the%20CAA%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20in%202020%2C%20told%20the%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Csurprising%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20find%20time%20earlier%20to%20notify%20the%20CAA%20rules%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Act%20has%20been%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20specific%20stay%2C%20the%20matter%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20heard%20for%20some%20time.%20In%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20rules%20have%20been%20notified%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20in%20respect%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20rules%2C%20there%20will%20be%20appropriate%20petitions%20filed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHegde%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20government%20wanted%20to%20notify%20these%20rules%20before%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20comes%20into%20play.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20advocate%20M.R.%20Shamshad%20also%20told%20PTI%20that%20the%20government%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20have%20exercised%20some%20restraint%E2%80%9D%20on%20notifying%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20implementation%20(of%20CAA)%20is%20concerned%2C%20this%20matter%20is%20already%20sub%20judice.%20On%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20the%20amendment%20of%202019%20is%20very%20discriminatory%20and%20arbitrary%20as%20it%20excludes%20people%20of%20a%20specific%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shamshad%20told%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CSince%20there%20is%20no%20stay%20on%20it%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20government%20should%20have%20exercised%20some%20restraint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20against%20law%20rocked%20Assam%2C%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20is%20well-known%20for%20the%20protests%20it%20sparked%20in%202019%20and%20early%202020%20that%20killed%20dozens%20and%20involved%20damages%20to%20property%20worth%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20began%20in%20early%202019%20in%20Assam%20when%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20passed%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerned%20that%20the%20Bill%20would%20cement%20the%20presence%20of%20Bangladeshi%20immigrants%20in%20the%20state%2C%20altering%20its%20demographic%20makeup%20and%20increasing%20competition%20for%20jobs%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-46997965%5C%22%3Eprotesters%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0torched%20BJP%20offices%20and%20surrounded%20the%20state%20secretariat%20on%20many%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20government%20went%20ahead%20with%20the%20Bill%2C%20enacting%20it%20into%20law%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20behind%20its%20persistence%20was%20that%20a%20census%20exercise%20conducted%20in%20Assam%20to%20sift%20citizens%20from%20illegal%20immigrants%20ended%20up%20classifying%20many%20Bengali%20Hindus%20%E2%80%93%20a%20significant%20source%20of%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20into%20the%20latter%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20also%20occurred%20outside%20Assam%2C%20although%20in%20this%20instance%20responding%20to%20the%20Act%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20religion%20to%20grant%20amnesty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20included%20a%20sit-in%20in%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20that%20went%20on%20for%20101%20days%20until%20it%20was%20removed%20by%20authorities%20in%20March%202020%20due%20to%20COVID-19%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20protests%2C%20a%20threat%20issued%20to%20an%20anti-CAA%20procession%20in%20Delhi%20by%20a%20BJP%20state%20legislator%20sparked%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdelhi-riots-amit-shah-muslims-delhi-police%5C%22%3Eriots%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20saw%20scores%20of%20deaths%20and%20hundreds%20of%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710168027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F07121932%2FUntitled-design-2021-12-07T121919.360.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmore-than-four-years-after-caa-was-passed-union-government-to-notify-rules%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20legal%20validity%20of%20the%20Act%20are%20pending%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmore-than-four-years-after-caa-was-passed-union-government-to-notify-rules%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%20chief%20urges%20'silencing%20the%20guns'%20in%20Gaza%20for%20Ramadan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710167785000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108401684%2Cimgsize-720280.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-chief-urges-silencing-the-guns-in-gaza-for-ramadan%2Farticleshow%2F108401603.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108401603.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20called%20Monday%20for%20%26quot%3Bsilencing%20the%20guns%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza%20in%20honor%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Muslim%20holy%20month%20of%20Ramadan.%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20called%20for%20a%20temporary%20ceasefire%20ahead%20of%20Ramadan%20but%20his%20call%20went%20unanswered%20as%20Muslims%20in%20Gaza%20marked%20the%20start%20of%20the%20one-month%20holiday%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-chief-urges-silencing-the-guns-in-gaza-for-ramadan%2Farticleshow%2F108401603.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-chief-urges-silencing-the-guns-in-gaza-for-ramadan%2Famp_articleshow%2F108401603.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-chief-urges-silencing-the-guns-in-gaza-for-ramadan%2Famp_articleshow%2F108401603.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Don't%20Hide%20Your%20Communal%20Prejudice%20Under%20the%20Cloak%20of%20Protecting%20Our%20Roads%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09110035%2F108329889.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ECan%20religious%20processions%20on%20roads%20be%20banned%20in%20India%3F%20Can%20such%20a%20law%20be%20implemented%20on%20events%20of%20different%20religions%20simultaneously%20and%20equally%3F%20The%20question%20does%20not%20have%20a%20particular%20answer%20but%20we%20can%20definitely%20sense%20the%20ferocity%20of%20the%20times%20in%20which%20the%20question%20is%20being%20posed.%20We%20need%20to%20listen%20carefully%20to%20the%20underlying%20voices%20behind%20the%20protest%20against%20agitations%20on%20roads%20or%20offering%20of%20namaz.%20We%20also%20need%20to%20see%20how%20far%20the%20political%20rhetoric%20related%20to%20roads%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%20The%20issue%20of%20toll%20tax%20or%20poor%20infrastructure%20of%20roads%20has%20not%20been%20raised%20as%20often%20and%20as%20vigorously%20as%20the%20matter%20of%20namaz%20on%20roads.%20Why%20is%20the%20question%20of%20road%20use%20so%20ferociously%20brought%20up%20only%20at%20the%20time%20of%20namaz%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20long%20been%20politics%20around%20roads%2C%20but%20the%20nature%20of%20this%20politics%20is%20different%20from%20communal%20politics.%20How%20to%20remove%20people%20from%20roads%20and%20how%20not%20to%20give%20them%20access%20to%20roads%20are%20matters%20decided%20by%20politics%20as%20well%20as%20class%20and%20power.%20Agricultural%20lands%20of%20farmers%20are%20acquired%20to%20make%20way%20for%20super%20expressways%20but%20once%20the%20road%20is%20ready%20for%20use%2C%20bullock%20carts%20and%20even%20bikes%20are%20not%20allowed%20on%20it.%20A%20bike%20cannot%20move%20in%20lanes%20made%20for%20vehicles%20moving%20at%20100%20km%2Fhr%20but%20why%20are%20lanes%20not%20constructed%20specifically%20for%20bullock%20carts%2C%20tractors%2C%20bikes%20and%20cycles%3F%20Fines%20are%20then%20imposed%20on%20two-wheelers%20and%20accidents%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20footpaths%20have%20vanished%20from%20roads%20in%20urban%20areas.%20Rights%20have%20been%20denied%20to%20pedestrians%20and%20here%20in%20Delhi%2C%20there%20is%20not%20a%20single%20lane%20for%20lakhs%20of%20cyclists.%20I%20am%20citing%20this%20example%20only%20to%20show%20that%20a%20road%20is%20not%20such%20a%20public%20and%20democratic%20space%20after%20all.%20In%20India%2C%20a%20particular%20class%20has%20dominated%20the%20roads%20%E2%80%93%20we%20call%20it%20the%20class%20of%20%E2%80%98car-wallahs%E2%80%99.%20A%20long%20campaign%20was%20run%20in%20a%20capital%20city%20like%20Delhi%20for%20making%20way%20for%20ambulances.%20There%20was%20some%20improvement%20but%20even%20today%20people%20forget%20to%20make%20way%20for%20an%20ambulance.%20When%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20convoy%20allowed%20an%20ambulance%20to%20pass%2C%20it%20was%20hyped%20as%20if%20a%20favour%20had%20been%20granted%20when%20it%20was%20something%20that%20should%20have%20naturally%20been%20done%20%E2%80%93%20no%20matter%20whose%20convoy%20it%20is%2C%20an%20ambulance%20has%20the%20first%20right%20to%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocratisation%20of%20roads%20in%20India%20has%20taken%20place%20in%20a%20very%20narrow%20sense.%20Even%20if%20we%20look%20at%20it%20only%20as%20a%20space%20for%20unhindered%20traffic%2C%20there%20is%20gross%20dishonesty%20here.%20However%2C%20one%20must%20understand%20that%20roads%20are%20not%20used%20only%20for%20going%20to%20office%20or%20a%20hospital.%20They%20are%20used%20for%20hundreds%20of%20democratic%20and%20religious%20activities.%20To%20enable%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20road%20show%2C%20roads%20are%20closed%20for%20several%20hours%20in%20a%20city.%20For%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20road%20show%20too%2C%20the%20route%20is%20planned%20and%20roads%20are%20closed.%20Road%20shows%20have%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20politics%20today.%20During%20election%20rallies%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20use%20and%20management%20of%20roads%20changes%20completely.%20Many%20roads%20in%20several%20states%20are%20affected%20due%20to%20rallies%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months%3B%20they%20remain%20closed%20and%20have%20diversions%20in%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Full%20Text%20%7C%20Christophe%20Jaffrelot%20on%20India's%20Spiral%20Into%20a%20'De-Facto%20Deeper%20State'%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffull-text-christophe-jaffrelot-on-indias-spiral-into-a-de-facto-deeper-state%5C%22%3EChristophe%20Jaffrelot%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20Spiral%20Into%20a%20%E2%80%98De-Facto%20Deeper%20State%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20road%20is%20closed%20for%20hours%20to%20allow%20a%20road%20show%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20does%20it%20cause%20the%20same%20unease%20as%20felt%20if%20namaz%20is%20offered%20on%20the%20road%3F%20Namaz%20lasts%20only%20for%2020%20minutes.%20Only%20a%20part%20of%20the%20road%20remains%20closed%20for%2030-40%20minutes.%20A%20similar%20instance%20is%20of%20people%20who%20use%20the%20road%20to%20travel%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Ganga%20or%20when%20they%20travel%20on%20foot%20to%20visit%20a%20traditional%20fair.%20When%20farmers%20were%20not%20coming%20to%20offer%20namaz%2C%20why%20was%20the%20road%20completely%20blocked%20for%20weeks%20to%20stop%20them%3F%20The%20borders%20of%20Delhi%20were%20closed%20from%20November%202020%20to%20November%202021%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20from%20entering%20Delhi.%20The%20government%20dismantled%20the%20very%20roads%20it%20built%20%E2%80%93%20from%20digging%20potholes%20to%20building%20cement%20walls%20%E2%80%93%20merely%20to%20stop%20the%20protesting%20farmers.%20Did%20it%20not%20cause%20discomfort%20to%20the%20people%3F%20A%20long%20march%20was%20organised%20for%20Maratha%20reservation%20in%20Maharashtra%20but%20neither%20were%20potholes%20dug%20in%20the%20road%20nor%20nails%20driven%20into%20it.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20religious%20and%20political%20use%20of%20roads%2C%20will%20the%20government%20be%20able%20to%20do%20politics%20as%20per%20its%20design%3F%20When%20the%20government%20reserves%20the%20right%20to%20do%20politics%20on%20roads%2C%20why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20public%20have%20rights%20too%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20cannot%20be%20one%20criterion%20to%20judge%20who%20the%20road%20will%20be%20closed%20for%20%E2%80%93%20neither%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%20nor%20politics.%20If%20the%20roads%20cannot%20be%20blocked%20for%20religious%20activities%2C%20how%20can%20they%20be%20closed%20for%20political%20rallies%3F%20Therefore%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20demand%20to%20ban%20programmes%20of%20all%20religions%20based%20on%20some%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20problems%20to%20civil%20society.%20Basically%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20supporters%20do%20not%20want%20democratic%20use%20of%20roads%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20by%20Muslims%20or%20farmers%20or%20any%20civil%20organisation.%20The%20communal%20and%20undemocratic%20political%20ideology%20behind%20the%20sudden%20awareness%20about%20roads%20needs%20to%20be%20carefully%20examined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20officer%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Tomar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdelhi-cop-suspended-after-video-of-kicking-muslims-offering-namaz-goes-viral%5C%22%3Ekicked%20worshippers%3C%2Fa%3E%20bowing%20in%20prostration.%20This%20was%20not%20something%20done%20under%20administrative%20responsibility%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mistake%20or%20an%20excess.%20Kicking%20from%20behind%20someone%20bowing%20in%20prostration%20is%20an%20act%20borne%20out%20of%20the%20womb%20of%20that%20ideology%20which%20is%20being%20spread%20night%20and%20day%20against%20Muslims.%20The%20action%20taken%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20against%20Tomar%20was%20not%20merely%20for%20kicking%20or%20slapping.%20Many%20people%20have%20understood%20this%20aspect%20and%20condemned%20it%20but%20many%20others%20are%20still%20feigning%20innocence.%20After%20saying%20Tomar%20was%20wrong%2C%20they%20immediately%20question%20why%20namaz%20was%20being%20offered%20on%20the%20road.%20As%20if%20whatever%20Tomar%20did%20was%20because%20of%20%E2%80%98this%20mistake%E2%80%99.%20It%20means%20a%20mistake%20had%20already%20been%20committed%20and%20Tomar%20resorted%20to%20kicking%20in%20order%20to%20rectify%20it.%20Many%20people%20are%20giving%20lectures%20on%20how%20namaz%20should%20not%20be%20offered%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20a%20blanket%20ban%20be%20imposed%20on%20all%20types%20of%20religious%20events%20on%20roads%3F%20That%20will%20more%20adversely%20affect%20hundreds%20of%20religious%20processions%20and%20events%20of%20Hindus%20which%20go%20on%20for%20several%20days.%20The%20desire%20to%20impose%20a%20ban%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20the%20demand%20for%20improved%20management%20of%20roads.%20But%20it%20only%20reflects%20the%20frustration%20towards%20a%20community%20and%20an%20insistence%20on%20spewing%20poison.%20The%20problem%20is%20not%20with%20namaz%20being%20offered%20on%20the%20road.%20How%20does%20it%20affect%20someone%20if%20a%20person%20offers%20namaz%20on%20a%20moving%20train%3F%20People%20have%20been%20doing%20so%20for%20ages%20and%20no%20one%20cared.%20But%20now%20a%20video%20is%20recorded%20which%20becomes%20the%20subject%20of%20debate%20on%20TV%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Enamazi%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20arrested.%20If%20someone%20offers%20it%20in%20the%20mall%2C%20a%20video%20is%20shot%2C%20hatred%20is%20spread%20over%20it%20and%20an%20uproar%20is%20created.%20Does%20offering%20namaz%20at%20a%20corner%20inside%20a%20mall%20or%20a%20coaching%20centre%20also%20lead%20to%20traffic%20jam%3F%20Recently%2C%20we%20saw%20passengers%20singing%20bhajans%20and%20raising%20slogans%20of%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20in%20planes%20carrying%20visitors%20to%20Ram%20temple.%20Was%20there%20uproar%20then%3F%20People%20have%20been%20doing%20bhajan-kirtan%20on%20trains%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20This%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20our%20train%20journeys.%20To%20ask%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20it%20sounds%20strange.%20Then%20people%20should%20not%20even%20play%20%3Cem%3Eantakshari%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20cannot%20separate%20roads%20in%20India%20from%20democratic%20and%20religious%20activities.%20Different%20types%20of%20barricades%20are%20set%20up%20on%20roads%20for%20millions%20of%20visitors%20pouring%20in%20to%20Prayagraj%20during%20the%20Kumbh.%20The%20administration%20adopts%20hundreds%20of%20methods%20using%20science%20and%20technology%20and%20spends%20millions%20of%20rupees%20on%20its%20management.%20Battalions%20of%20personnel%20are%20deployed.%20Many%20roads%20are%20completely%20closed.%20Some%20are%20closed%20halfway%20and%20many%20diversions%20are%20placed%20too.%20Whether%20it%20is%20a%20fair%20or%20Ganga-snan%2C%20the%20people%20take%20the%20same%20route%20and%20cover%20several%20kilometres%20on%20foot.%20Today%2C%20the%20administration%20does%20this%20work%20more%20efficiently%20as%20opposed%20to%20two%20decades%20ago.%20With%20time%2C%20the%20management%20of%20Kumbh%20is%20getting%20better.%20But%20to%20say%20that%20Kumbh%20can%20be%20separated%20from%20the%20road%20is%20absurdity.%20What%20was%20done%20to%20the%20namazis%20is%20the%20sick%20mentality%20which%20is%20enjoying%20it%20secretly.%20They%20know%20that%20they%20are%20only%20talking%20about%20stopping%20%3Cem%3Enamaz%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20rest%20is%20only%20a%20charade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hate%20Speech%3A%20How%20to%20Promote%20Amity%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhate-speech-how-to-promote-amity%5C%22%3EHate%20Speech%3A%20How%20to%20Promote%20Amity%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Kanwar%20Yatra%2C%20roads%20are%20closed%20for%20a%20month.%20Tents%20are%20set%20up%20by%20the%20road%20side.%20One%20cannot%20lecture%20on%20how%20tents%20should%20not%20be%20set%20up%20on%20the%20roadside%20during%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20and%20roads%20should%20not%20be%20blocked%20with%20barricades%20in%20front%20of%20the%20tents.%20Cities%20no%20longer%20have%20space%20to%20set%20up%20tents%20away%20from%20the%20road.%20So%20tents%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20pitched%20on%20the%20roads.%20Kanwars%20travel%20on%20foot.%20Roads%20need%20to%20be%20closed%20for%20them%20as%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20accident%20due%20to%20fast-moving%20vehicles%20and%20despite%20arrangements%2C%20kanwars%20get%20killed.%20Today%2C%20the%20arrangements%20have%20got%20better%20on%20these%20very%20roads%20and%20the%20attitude%20towards%20kanwars%20has%20also%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20when%20I%20arrived%20in%20Delhi%2C%20people%20looked%20scared%20of%20these%20Kanwar%20Yatris%20because%20they%20had%20sticks%20in%20their%20hands.%20Looking%20at%20them%20carrying%20batons%20and%20hockey%20sticks%2C%20people%20used%20to%20remark%20that%20they%20are%20not%20pilgrims%20and%20they%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20religion.%20They%20were%20called%20goons%20and%20scoundrels.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20news%20coverage%20of%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20in%20English%20media%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20you%20will%20find%20similar%20references.%20I%20began%20to%20view%20kanwars%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20someone%20in%20Delhi%20with%20my%20backdrop.%20In%20Bihar%20too%20the%20kanwars%20used%20to%20march%20on%20foot%20but%20no%20one%20made%20such%20remarks.%20Why%20in%20Delhi%3F%20I%20used%20to%20wonder%20that%20all%20that%20walking%20must%20make%20their%20feet%20sore%2C%20then%20why%20were%20such%20things%20said%20about%20them%3F%20Kanwars%20have%20sticks%20in%20their%20hands%20because%20they%20cannot%20walk%20without%20it.%20Secondly%2C%20there%20was%20less%20security%20on%20the%20roads%20earlier%20and%20more%20accidents%20were%20caused%20because%20roads%20were%20not%20closed.%20Therefore%2C%20kanwars%20used%20to%20travel%20in%20groups%20and%20in%20case%20of%20an%20accident%2C%20they%20would%20enter%20a%20brawl%20with%20the%20car%20or%20truck%20driver%20and%20resort%20to%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoads%20are%20closed%20for%20a%20month%20for%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20and%20routes%20are%20altered.%20People%20face%20problems%20but%20little%20can%20be%20done%20to%20avoid%20it.%20Can%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20be%20completely%20prohibited%2C%20arguing%20that%20all%20kinds%20of%20religious%20events%20should%20be%20disallowed%20on%20roads%3F%20It%20would%20be%20foolish%20to%20say%20so%2C%20and%20an%20exaggeration.%20The%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20held%20%E2%80%93%20on%20foot%20and%20on%20the%20roads.%20So%2C%20those%20who%20are%20pointing%20out%20at%20namaz%20and%20lecturing%20on%20how%20religious%20events%20should%20be%20disallowed%20on%20roads%20are%20deliberately%20ignoring%20all%20these%20complexities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20police%20administration%20has%20made%20better%20arrangements%20for%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra.%20Problems%20faced%20by%20the%20kanwars%20and%20conflicts%20have%20also%20reduced%20as%20compared%20to%20before.%20The%20sale%20of%20meat%20is%20prohibited%20during%20the%20Yatra%20which%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20road.%20But%20which%20community%20is%20affected%20by%20it%20the%20most%3F%20People%20accepted%20the%20decision%20any%20way.%20Does%20the%20government%20grant%20them%20a%20month%E2%80%99s%20expenses%20in%20return%3F%20A%20large%20number%20of%20Muslims%20also%20serve%20food%20during%20Kanwar%20Yatras.%20Many%20such%20incidents%20of%20social%20harmony%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20the%20media.%20We%20should%20not%20forget%20that%20there%20has%20also%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20politicisation%20of%20the%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra%2C%20but%20even%20during%20Ganpati%20Puja%20and%20Durga%20Puja%2C%20no%20such%20law%20prohibiting%20religious%20events%20on%20roads%20can%20be%20implemented.%20Is%20it%20possible%20for%20the%20road%20to%20not%20be%20closed%20for%20idol%20immersion%3F%20The%20main%20road%20as%20well%20as%20the%20road%20within%20a%20locality%20is%20bound%20to%20get%20blocked%20for%20puja%20events.%20Pandals%20are%20set%20up%20in%20the%20parks%20of%20housing%20societies.%20Our%20police%20has%20made%20improvements%20in%20the%20arrangements%20by%20collaborating%20with%20fair%20and%20puja%20committees.%20Several%20issues%20have%20been%20addressed%20but%20there%20is%20still%20more%20scope%20for%20improvement.%20However%2C%20if%20a%20demand%20is%20made%20for%20prohibiting%20pandals%20on%20roads%20during%20Durga%20Puja%2C%20the%20police%20will%20spend%20all%20its%20time%20removing%20pandals%20during%20the%20festival%20and%20it%20will%20only%20lead%20to%20tension%20at%20various%20places.%20Now%2C%20many%20organising%20committees%20are%20working%20alongside%20the%20police%20to%20ensure%20that%20traffic%20is%20affected%20as%20little%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20are%20strictly%20against%20offering%20namaz%20on%20the%20road%20should%20lecture%20the%20BJP%20and%C2%A0Bajrang%20Dal%20instead%20and%20ask%20them%20to%20stop%20organising%20Shobha%20Yatras%20on%20Ram%20Navami.%20They%20should%20be%20asked%20to%20not%20close%20roads%20for%20the%20yatra%20and%20not%20allow%20DJs%20to%20play%20loud%20music.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20they%20pay%20attention%20to%20all%20the%20problems%20and%20issues%20of%20the%20roads%20when%20they%20insist%20on%20taking%20the%20procession%20through%20localities%20of%20another%20community%3F%20The%20administration%20has%20not%20given%20permission%20for%20Shobha%20Yatra%20in%20view%20of%20the%20tension%20at%20several%20places%2C%20but%20granted%20permission%20at%20other%20places.%20Even%20in%20such%20matters%20the%20decision%20rests%20with%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20can%20there%20be%20a%20ban%20on%20Ram%20Navami%20processions%20in%20all%20the%20states%20simultaneously%3F%20Are%20you%20not%20aware%20that%20a%20particular%20party%20makes%20a%20huge%20investment%20during%20Ram%20Navami%20processions%3F%20There%20is%20scope%20for%20improvement%20in%20these%20yatras.%20The%20volume%20of%20music%20played%20by%20the%20DJ%20can%20be%20lowered%20and%20a%20fixed%20route%20can%20be%20arranged%2C%20which%20might%20have%20already%20been%20done.%20But%20to%20ask%20for%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20taking%20out%20such%20processions%20sounds%20weird.%20The%20police%20and%20administration%20toil%20night%20and%20day%20during%20the%20time%20of%20Ram%20Navami%20in%20organising%20the%20yatras.%20The%20officials%20do%20not%20go%20home%20for%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELangar%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebhandara%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20not%20merely%20religious%20activities%20in%20Delhi%20but%20some%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20things%20about%20this%20city.%20It%20has%20inspired%20other%20cities%20to%20follow%20suit.%20Even%20during%20bhandaras%2C%20traffic%20gets%20affected%20but%20for%20any%20Bhandara%2C%20roads%20need%20to%20be%20used.%20The%20person%20organising%20the%20bhandara%20should%20seek%20the%20help%20of%20the%20local%20police%2C%20but%20there%20is%20only%20so%20much%20the%20police%20can%20do.%20How%20many%20times%20can%20permission%20be%20sought%3F%20Ultimately%2C%20it%20is%20for%20the%20people%20to%20learn%20to%20organise%20bhandara%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20there%20is%20minimum%20disruption%20in%20traffic.%20But%20when%20a%20hundred%20or%20two%20hundred%20people%20are%20involved%2C%20disruption%20is%20bound%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Travelling%20Under%20the%20Shadow%20of%20Saffron%20Flags%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ftravelling-under-the-shadow-of-saffron-flags%5C%22%3ETravelling%20Under%20the%20Shadow%20of%20Saffron%20Flags%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20should%20also%20look%20at%20bhandaras%20from%20a%20human%20perspective.%20India%20is%20a%20poor%20country.%20People%20have%20little%20to%20eat%20before%20leaving%20for%20work.%20After%20toiling%20the%20entire%20day%2C%20they%20get%20hungry.%20A%20bhandara%20in%20such%20a%20situation%20saves%20the%20day%20for%20them.%20The%20%3Cem%3Ebhandara%3C%2Fem%3E%20host%20also%20wants%20people%20to%20come.%20And%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20meal%20delicious%3F%20In%20Delhi%20and%20other%20cities%2C%20people%20stop%20buses%20and%20offer%20refreshing%20drinks%20to%20passengers%20during%20summer.%20It%20causes%20disruption%20in%20traffic.%20The%20residents%20of%20cities%20adjust%20to%20these%20problems.%20Some%20arrangements%20can%20be%20made%20to%20reduce%20the%20problems%20that%20arise%20but%20if%20a%20langar%20or%20bhandara%20is%20not%20held%20on%20a%20road%2C%20where%20else%20will%20it%20be%20held%3F%20Bhandara%20is%20for%20passers-by.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20banquet%20which%20is%20set%20up%20indoors%20and%20invitations%20are%20extended.%20The%20American%20society%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20such%20activities.%20Therefore%2C%20such%20problems%20do%20not%20arise%20there.%20However%2C%20the%20Indian%20community%20members%20settled%20there%20are%20taking%20out%20processions%20on%20bulldozers%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20about%20the%20road%20here.%20It%20is%20about%20namaz%2C%20and%20the%20person%20offering%20namaz%20who%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20Since%20one%20cannot%20justify%20the%20incident%20of%20kicking%2C%20one%20has%20started%20denouncing%20the%20act%20of%20offering%20namaz%20on%20the%20road.%20One%20only%20wants%20to%20continue%20humiliating%20and%20suppressing%20a%20community.%20Have%20we%20forgotten%20the%20Gurugram%20incident%3F%20People%20were%20not%20offering%20namaz%20on%20the%20road%20there.%20Namaz%20was%20being%20offered%20in%20a%20ground.%20Yet%20people%20came%20to%20protest.%20At%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20debate%20is%20not%20the%20road%2C%20but%20Muslims.%20Their%20religious%20rights%20are%20continuously%20being%20attacked.%20At%20many%20places%2C%20offering%20namaz%20on%20the%20streets%20has%20been%20banned%20but%20events%20of%20other%20religions%20are%20allowed%20to%20take%20place.%20Community%20prayers%20on%20Eid%20are%20not%20held%20at%20many%20places%20because%20if%20thousands%20of%20people%20pray%20together%2C%20the%20roads%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20used.%20Therefore%2C%20namaz%20is%20now%20being%20offered%20in%20shifts.%20It%20is%20not%20as%20if%20any%20community%20is%20stubbornly%20offering%20namaz%20on%20the%20road.%20They%20do%20so%20because%20they%20are%20facing%20problems.%20But%20offering%20namaz%20in%20parks%20has%20been%20made%20problematic%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20better%20that%20we%20learn%20to%20live%20together%20and%20move%20forward%20with%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20each%20other.%20We%20need%20to%20reduce%20the%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20religious%20events%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20improve%20the%20system%20and%20stop%20nurturing%20hatred.%20The%20Indian%20administration%20has%20made%20several%20major%20achievements%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20has%20improved%20arrangements.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20hatred%20that%20is%20being%20spread%20left%2C%20right%20and%20centre%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religious%20activities.%20This%20hatred%20will%20give%20rise%20to%20more%20Chetan%20Singhs%20and%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Tomars%2C%20who%20will%20either%20go%20to%20jail%20or%20be%20suspended.%20You%20can%20defend%20them%20only%20by%20becoming%20a%20crowd%20because%20you%20are%20well%20aware%20that%20it%20is%20neither%20logical%20nor%20socially%20acceptable.%20It%20is%20neither%20acceptable%20to%20religion%20nor%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20True%2C%20that%20you%20are%20in%20power%2C%20you%20have%20the%20crowd%2C%20so%20you%20can%20do%20whatever%20you%20want%2C%20but%20you%20do%20know%20where%20the%20problem%20lies.%20The%20problem%20is%20not%20in%20offering%20namaz%20on%20the%20road%20but%20in%20the%20way%20someone%20offering%20namaz%20is%20looked%20at.%20It%20is%20better%20one%20accepts%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Hindi%20original%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fravish-kumar%5C%22%3ERavish%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%20You%20can%20find%20him%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40ravishkumar.official%5C%22%3E%40ravishkumar.official%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710167417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09110035%2F108329889.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdont-hide-your-communal-prejudice-under-the-cloak-of-protecting-our-roads%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Roads%20are%20regularly%20used%20for%20religious%20and%20political%20purposes.%20It%20is%20not%20about%20the%20road%20here.%20It%20is%20about%20namaz%2C%20and%20the%20person%20offering%20namaz%20who%20is%20a%20Muslim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdont-hide-your-communal-prejudice-under-the-cloak-of-protecting-our-roads%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jerusalem%20Muslims%20were%20promised%20freedom%20to%20worship%20this%20Ramadan%20%E2%80%93%20I%20watched%20them%20being%20turned%20away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710167280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-ramadan-jerusalem_6487050.jpg%3F20240311165702%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjerusalem-muslims-were-promised-freedom-to-worship-this-ramadan-8211-i-watched-them-being-turned-away-13092684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20should%20be%20one%20of%20the%20great%20moments%20in%20the%20Islamic%20calendar.%20When%20a%20month%20of%20prayer%2C%20fasting%20and%20ultimately%20celebration%20begins.%20But%20Ramadan%20has%20started%20this%20year%20in%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20resentment%2C%20fear%20and%20anger%20for%20Palestinian%20Muslims%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A422%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjerusalem-muslims-were-promised-freedom-to-worship-this-ramadan-i-watched-them-being-turned-away-13092684%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjerusalem-muslims-were-promised-freedom-to-worship-this-ramadan-i-watched-them-being-turned-away-13092684%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjerusalem-muslims-were-promised-freedom-to-worship-this-ramadan-i-watched-them-being-turned-away-13092684%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Jat%20Leader%20Brijendra%20Singh%20Quit%20BJP%20to%20Join%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11185254%2FUntitled-design-39.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20day%20after%20quitting%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20joining%20Congress%2C%20Jat%20leader%20and%20Hisar%20member%20of%20parliament%20Brijendra%20Singh%20said%20his%20decision%20to%20leave%20the%20party%20was%20not%20a%20knee-jerk%20reaction%2C%20but%20it%20was%20building%20up%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20this%2C%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20socio-political%20dynamics%20of%20his%20constituency%20or%20his%20state%20revolves%20widely%20around%20Kisan%20(farmer)%2C%20jawan%20(solider)%2C%20and%20khiladi%20(sportsperson).%20But%20the%20interest%20of%20all%20these%20sections%20was%20widely%20overlooked%20under%20the%20BJP%20regime%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%20the%20way%20the%20current%20government%20mishandled%20their%20concerns%20was%20even%20more%20unfortunate%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Brijendra%20while%20referring%20to%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20row%20over%20agniveer%20scheme%20curtailing%20service%20years%20in%20armed%20forces%20and%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20female%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20protest%20against%20former%20wresting%20federation%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20over%20harassment%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelonging%20to%20the%20Jat%20icon%20Chhotu%20Ram%20family%2C%20his%20father%20Birender%20Singh%20too%20is%20hailed%20as%20an%20important%20Jat%20leader%20of%20the%20state.%20He%20remained%20in%20Congress%20for%20decades%20before%20joining%20BJP%20in%202014%20and%20later%20served%20as%20Union%20minister%20in%20the%20first%20Modi%20cabinet%20between%202014-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20father%20took%20retirement%20from%20electoral%20politics%20in%20the%20last%20general%20election%2C%20Bijendra%20Singh%20stepped%20into%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20shoes%20after%20leaving%20his%20two-decades-long%20stint%20in%20Indian%20Administrative%20Services%20(IAS)%20and%20won%20parliamentary%20election%20from%20Hisar%20that%20his%20father%20once%20represented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20him%2C%20ideologically%20speaking%20he%20always%20felt%20like%20a%20misfit%20in%20the%20BJP%20since%20the%20beginning.%20Then%20things%20started%20building%20up%20against%20the%20section%20of%20voters%20his%20family%20represented%20for%20long%2C%20which%20he%20could%20not%20overlook%20due%20to%20his%20family%20legacy%20and%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitically%20too%2C%20he%20said%20they%20had%20problems%20within%20BJP.%20He%20said%20they%20conveyed%20many%20times%20their%20unhappiness%20over%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20alliance%20with%20the%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(another%20Jat-oriented%20political%20party%20under%20the%20extended%20Chautala%20family)%20but%20the%20party%20stayed%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20father%20during%20a%20rally%20in%20their%20home%20town%20Jind%20last%20October%20had%20clearly%20stated%20that%20if%20this%20alliance%20continued%2C%20they%20would%20part%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20section%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20were%20also%20against%20the%20alliance%20but%20nobody%20was%20ready%20to%20take%20action%20against%20it%20and%20then%20they%20had%20to%20take%20a%20call%20somehow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20they%20were%20against%20the%20BJP%20post-assembly%20polls%20alliance%20(which%20came%20into%20existence%20after%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls)%2C%20he%20replied%20that%20how%20it%20can%20be%20tolerable%20that%20the%20party%20which%20won%20seats%20by%20targeting%20BJP%20is%20now%20sharing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAsk%20BJP%20leaders%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20they%20were%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20alliance%20either.%20It%20is%20just%20that%20we%20spoke%20against%20it%20publically%20and%20they%20could%20not%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hit%20out%20at%20JJP%20saying%20that%20their%20claims%20that%20they%20represent%20farmers%E2%80%99%20interests%20are%20hollow.%20They%20only%20enjoyed%20power%20in%20alliance%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20he%20believed%20the%20BJP%20was%20insensitive%20to%20issues%20of%20farmers%2C%20youth%20and%20wrestlers%20during%20their%20tenure%2C%20he%20replied%20that%20when%20a%20government%20enjoys%20a%20majority%20(in%20Parliament)%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20believe%20that%20whatever%20they%20are%20doing%20is%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20what%20was%20the%20need%20to%20bring%20an%20ordinance%20for%20three%20farm%20bills%20in%202020%20which%20otherwise%20had%20wider%20consequences%20on%20the%20agri%20market%20in%20India%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThings%20would%20have%20been%20different%20if%20these%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20later%20withdrawn%20by%20BJP%20after%20year%20year-long%20farm%20protest%20outside%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20were%20first%20discussed%20with%20thread-bare%20clarity%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20parliament%20before%20its%20implementation.%20At%20least%20no%20one%20would%20have%20complained%20that%20all%20stakeholders%20were%20not%20involved%20in%20decision-making%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Birendra%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20such%20a%20one-sided%20decision%20only%20created%20suspicion%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20people%20and%20that%20is%20why%20the%20entire%20farming%20community%20in%20north%20Indian%20states%20were%20up%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20forced%20it%20to%20withdraw%20these%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20views%20on%20Haryana%20police%E2%80%99s%20latest%20action%20to%20halt%20another%20Delhi%20march%20by%20farmers%2C%20he%20said%20the%20action%20was%20condemnable.%20It%20appeared%20as%20if%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20borders%20turned%20into%20national%20borders.%20He%20said%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20BJP-JJP%20government%20in%20Haryana%20was%20missing%20especially%20when%20farmer%20issues%20needed%20open%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrijendra%20said%20agrarian%20distress%20was%20on%20the%20rise%20ever%20since%20the%20Indian%20economy%20adopted%20liberalised%20economic%20policies%20in%20the%2090s.%20%E2%80%9COur%20family%20has%20been%20advocating%20for%20long%20for%20the%20wide-scale%20agrarian%20reforms%20which%20ensure%20stable%20income%20and%20value%20addition%20to%20farmers%20earning%20along%20with%20protection%20to%20their%20land%20and%20cattle%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20agriculture%20issues%20have%20structural%20problems%20and%20the%20Congress%20party%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20would%20address%20it%20deeply%20if%20he%20comes%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20hopes%20to%20consolidate%20the%20Jat%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Brijendra%E2%80%99s%20father%20Birender%20Singh%20too%20might%20join%20Congress%20in%20a%20few%20days.%20He%20had%20been%20one%20of%20the%20tallest%20jat%20leaders%20of%20Congress%20for%20decades%20before%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirender%20Singh%20accompanied%20his%20son%20when%20he%20joined%20Congress%20on%20Sunday%2C%20March%2010%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Congress%20national%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20hoped%20that%20father-son%20due%20might%20help%20them%20consolidate%20the%20important%20Jat%20vote%20in%20Haryana%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20whose%20polity%20is%20sharply%20divided%20between%20Jats%20and%20non-Jats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20faultline%20has%20sharpened%20further%20ever%20since%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Haryana%20post%20in%20the%20Modi%20era%20due%20to%20the%20consolidation%20of%20non-Jats%20in%20their%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Kushal%20Pal%20Singh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20it%20is%20being%20speculated%20that%20Brijendra%20Singh%20left%20BJP%20over%20his%20fear%20of%20getting%20replaced%20by%20Kuldeep%20Bishnoi%20from%20Hisar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20him%2C%20more%20than%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20loss%2C%20his%20joining%20will%20benefit%20Congress%2C%20given%20that%20his%20family%20still%20holds%20influence%20in%20certain%20pockets%20of%20Haryana%2C%20which%20remained%20loyal%20to%20them%20whether%20they%20were%20in%20Congress%20or%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20help%20Congress%20to%20consolidate%20its%20Jat%20vote%20bank%20and%20perform%20better%20from%20drastic%20defeat%20during%20the%20last%20polls%20when%20it%20lost%20all%2010%20seats%20in%20Haryana%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20Congress%20lost%20a%20few%20seats%20like%20Rohtak%20with%20small%20margins.%20Things%20might%20turn%20different%20for%20the%20party%20in%20this%20election%20due%20to%20changing%20political%20equations%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20alliance%20with%20AAP%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20poll%20pact%2C%20Congress%20is%20fighting%20nine%20seats%20while%20AAP%20has%20been%20given%20one%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710165564000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11185254%2FUntitled-design-39.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-jat-leader-brijendra-singh-quit-bjp-to-join-congress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singh%2C%20who%20is%20considered%20an%20important%20Jat%20leader%20of%20Haryana%2C%20hails%20from%20the%20widely%20known%20Chhotu%20Ram%20family.%20He%20was%20in%20Congress%20for%20decades%20before%20joining%20the%20BJP%20in%202