%20Nari%20Shakti%20(women%20power)!%20We%20were%20enticed%20with%20Beti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%20(save%20the%20girl%20child%2C%20educate%20the%20girl%20child)!%20We%20were%20promised%20Vikas%20(development)!%20We%20were%20promised%20cheaper%20gas%2C%20cheaper%20petrol!%20We%20were%20promised%20a%20%245%20trillion%20economy!%20We%20were%20promised%20smart%20cities!%20We%20were%20promised%20that%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20would%20double!%20We%20were%20promised%20%E2%80%98Housing%20for%20All%E2%80%99%20by%202022!%20We%20were%20promised%20protection%20of%20our%20borders%20and%20the%20end%20of%20terrorist%20activity!%203%20And%20what%20did%20we%20get%3F%20We%20got%20a%20lost%20decade!%20All%20the%20promises%20were%20jumlas%20%E2%80%A6%20empty%20promises!%20Power%20now%20rests%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20two%20or%20three%20leaders%2C%20who%20are%20less%20and%20less%20accountable%20to%20the%20voters%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20declaration%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20press%20release%2C%20the%20declaration%20was%20earlier%20adopted%20and%20released%20on%20February%2021%20at%20the%20Kittur%20Fort%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20about%2050%20kilometres%20from%20Belagavi%20in%20Karnataka%20%E2%80%94%20as%20part%20of%20an%20event%20commemorating%20200%20years%20of%20Kittur%20Rani%20Chennamma%E2%80%99s%20revolt%20against%20the%20British%20Empire.As%20per%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(previously%20called%20Twitter)%20by%20social%20activist%20Shabnam%20Hashmi%2C%202500%20women%20participated%20in%20the%20event%20at%20Kittur%20Fort%20%E2%80%9Cto%20expose%20the%20misdeeds%20of%20the%20present%20regime%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOver%202500%20women%20release%20The%20Kittur%20Declaration%20pledging%20to%20expose%20the%20misdeeds%20of%20the%20present%20regime%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20and%20d