ould%20ask%20her%20why%20she%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20making%20this%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Cem%3Edaadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20would%20sit%20with%20this%20iron%20%3Cem%3Ekadhai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(large%20vessel)%20every%20week%2C%20and%20spend%20hours%20stirring%20the%20oil%2C%20adding%2013%20ingredients%20one%20by%20one.%20She%20used%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20I%20would%20realise%20its%20worth%20after%20growing%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nidhi%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESure%20enough%2C%20just%20as%20the%20wise%20woman%20had%20predicted%2C%20Nidhi%20turned%20to%20her%20daadi%E2%80%99s%20recipe%20when%20she%20faced%20the%20massive%20challenge%20of%20hairfall.%20The%20duo%20made%20the%20oil%20together%2C%20which%20took%20an%20entire%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20tremendous%20hair%20fall.%20After%20using%20it%20for%20about%20two-three%20months%2C%20we%20found%20that%20our%20hairfall%20had%20greatly%20reduced%20and%20our%20hair%20was%20growing.%20I%20started%20making%20it%20for%20my%20daughter%20and%20our%20domestic%20help%2C%20who%20also%20found%20it%20greatly%20effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Tuteja-Dua%20family%20shifted%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Gurugram%2C%20into%20an%20apartment%20complex.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20Nidhi%20would%20find%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20shape%20to%20her%20desires.%20She%20found%20women%20here%20who%20were%20running%20small%20businesses%20from%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20mothers%2C%20Nidhi%2C%20too%2C%20had%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20have%20a%20flourishing%20career.%20When%20she%20heard%20about%20these%20women%2C%20she%20found%20her%20window.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20join%20the%20office%20again.%20I%20missed%20my%20financial%20freedom%20and%20kept%20thinking%20of%20what%20I%20could%20do%20to%20reclaim%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajni%2C%20who%20had%20spent%20her%20life%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20children%2C%20followed%20by%20her%20grandchildren%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20harbour%20such%20aspirations%2C%20she%20shares.%20But%20when%20Nidhi%20asked%20for%20her%20help%2C%20the%20indulgent%20mother-in-law%2C%20went%20all%20in%20to%20support%20her%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20started%20distributing%20the%20oil%20to%20women%20in%20our%20society.%20To%20our%20surprise%2C%20they%20kept%20coming%20back%20for%20more.%20In%20fact%2C%20our%20doorbell%20used%20to%20keep%20ringing%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20they%20would%20pack%20the%20oil%20in%20normal%20bottles%20with%20a%20sticker.%20The%20first%20batch%20of%20one%20litre%20was%20made%20on%20a%20small%20kadhai%20and%20sold%2010%20bottles.%20As%20soon%20as%20Nidhi%20posted%20on%20a%20Whatsapp%20group%2C%20they%20were%20sold%20out%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20925px)%20100vw%2C%20925px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22925%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi%20and%20Rajni%20started%20making%20the%20hair%20oil%20for%20their%20own%20use%20in%202020%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491.jpeg%20925w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-234x300.jpeg%20234w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-500x641.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-768x985.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-150x192.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343999%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221186%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENidhi%20and%20Rajni%20started%20making%20the%20hair%20oil%20for%20their%20own%20use%20in%202020%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20they%20had%20given%20their%20oil%20to%20over%20200%20people%20in%20the%20society%2C%20the%20software%20engineer%20realised%20the%20viability%20of%20her%20business.%20As%20orders%20increased%2C%20they%20bought%20bigger%20vessels%2C%20a%20five%20litre%20and%2010%20litre%20kadhai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20increase%20their%20presence%20and%20set%20up%20an%20Instagram%20account%2C%20%E2%80%98Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%E2%80%99.%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20Rajat%2C%20is%20a%20digital%20marketeer%20and%20helped%20her%20with%20her%20social%20media%20presence.%20One%20of%20their%20reels%20went%20viral%2C%20and%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20orders.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20they%20had%20100%20orders%20on%20their%20hands!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNidhi%20was%20overwhelmed%20and%20wondered%20how%20we%20would%20fulfil%20so%20many%20orders.%20I%20reassured%20her%20that%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20Nidhi%20faced%20initially%20was%20mental%2C%20as%20she%20wondered%20if%20they%20could%20succeed%2C%20and%20build%20a%20business%20from%20home.%20Having%20worked%20in%20a%20corporate%20environment%2C%20she%20worried%20about%20the%20intricacies%20involved%20in%20setting%20up%20a%20business%20from%20scratch%2C%20especially%20one%20that%20is%20very%20laborious%20and%20customer-centric.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worried%20if%20this%20hair%20oil%20would%20work%20on%20everyone.%20My%20idea%20was%20to%20help%20people%20manage%20hair%20fall.%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20doing%20a%20business%20and%20was%20unsure%20of%20facing%20everyting%20that%20it%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20candidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother-in-law%20stood%20by%20her%20like%20a%20rock%20and%20defied%20her%20age%20to%20literally%20burn%20the%20midnight%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20win%20for%20the%20duo%20was%20successfully%20fulfilling%20the%20100%20orders.%20From%20that%20day%20on%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334496%2Fkashmir-rukhsaar-sayeed-masterchef-india-chef-khalis-frozen-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-woman%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20worked%20day%20and%20night%20to%20make%20the%20oil.%20Till%20September%202023%2C%20they%20made%20the%20oil%20at%20home%20and%20managed%20manufacturing%2C%20packaging%2C%20customer%20support%2C%20social%20media%2C%20and%20website%20all%20by%20themselves.%20After%20the%20success%20of%20their%20oil%2C%20they%20introduced%20a%20shampoo%20using%20Rajni%E2%80%99s%20recipe%2C%20a%20conditioner%2C%20scalp%20scrub%20and%20comb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20have%20over%208%2C000%20orders%20per%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20secret%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20938px)%20100vw%2C%20938px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi's%20Grandma%20Secret%20operates%20out%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Panchkula%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312.jpeg%20938w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-176x300.jpeg%20176w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-500x853.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-768x1310.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-900x1536.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-150x256.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343996%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandma%20Secret%20operates%20out%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Panchkula%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20oil%20sell%20out%20and%20attract%20repeat%20customers%3F%20Nidhi%20states%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98100%20percent%20natural%20and%20homemade%E2%80%99.%20The%20oil%20is%20made%20using%20a%20secret%20mix%20of%2013%20herbs%20with%20coconut%20oil%20as%20the%20base.%20Without%20revealing%20the%20secret%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20Nidhi%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20the%20oil%20in%20an%20iron%20kadhai%2C%20add%20coconut%20oil%2C%20and%20add%20each%20of%20the%20ingredients%20one%20by%20one.%20We%20cook%20it%20for%20at%20least%20two%20hours%20after%20which%20we%20rest%20it%20for%208-10%20hours.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20we%20strain%20it%20using%20a%20cotton%20cloth%20and%20reheat%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20then%20cooled%2C%20strained%20and%20packed%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ingredients%20include%20curry%20leaf%20and%20aloe%20vera%20gel%20among%20others.%20They%20make%20about%20100%20litres%20of%20oil%20in%20two%20days%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamaljeet%20Arya%2C%20one%20of%20their%20customers%2C%20says%20that%20the%20hair%20oil%20and%20shampoo%20have%20had%20a%20tremendous%20impact%20for%20her.%20She%20faced%20hairfall%20issues%20as%20she%20is%20peri-menopausal%20and%20has%20thyroid%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20many%20different%20products%20over%20the%20years%20but%20nothing%20really%20worked.%20I%20found%20out%20about%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20G